20in%20most%20cases%20is%20simple.%20Send%20her%20to%20college%2C--to%20almost%20any%20college.%20Send%20her%20because%20there%20is%20no%20other%20place%20where%20between%20eighteen%20and%20twenty-two%20she%20is%20so%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20genuinely%20good%20time.%20Merely%20for%20good%20times%2C%20for%20romance%2C%20for%20society%2C%20college%20life%20offers%20unequalled%20opportunities.%20Of%20course%20no%20idle%20person%20can%20possibly%20be%20happy%2C%20even%20for%20a%20day%2C%20nor%20she%20who%20makes%20a%20business%20of%20trying%20to%20amuse%20herself.%20For%20full%20happiness%2C%20though%20its%20springs%20are%20within%2C%20we%20want%20health%20and%20friends%20and%20work%20and%20objects%20of%20aspiration.%20%22We%20live%20by%20admiration%2C%20hope%2C%20and%20love%2C%22%20says%20Wordsworth.%20The%20college%20abounds%20in%20all%20three.%20In%20the%20college%20time%20new%20powers%20are%20sprouting%2C%20and%20intelligence%2C%20merriment%2C%20truthfulness%20and%20generosity%20are%20more%20natural%20than%20the%20opposite%20qualities%20often%20become%20in%20later%20years.%20An%20exhilarating%20atmosphere%20pervades%20the%20place.%20We%20who%20are%20in%20it%20all%20the%20time%20feel%20that%20we%20live%20at%20the%20fountain%20of%20perpetual%20youth%2C%20and%20those%20who%20take%20but%20a%20four%20years%26%2339%3B%20bath%20in%20it%20become%20more%20cheerful%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20full%20of%20promise%20than%20they%20are%20ever%20likely%20to%20find%20themselves%20again%3B%20for%20a%20college%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20compendium%20of%20the%20things%20that%20most%20men%20long%20for.%20It%20is%20usually%20planted%20in%20a%20beautiful%20spot%2C%20the%20charm%20of%20trees%20and%20water%20being%20added%20to%20stately%20buildings%20and%20stimulating%20works%20of%20art.%20Venerable%20associations%20of%20the%20past%20hallow%20its%20halls.%20Leaders%20in%20the%20stirring%20world%20of%20to-day%20return%20at%20each%20commencement%20to%20share%20the%20fresh%20life%20of%20the%20new%20class.%20Books%2C%20pictures%2C%20music%2C%20collections%2C%20appliances%20in%20every%20field%2C%20learned%20teachers%2C%20mirthful%20friends%2C%20athletics%20for%20holidays%2C%20the%20best%20words%20of%20the%20best%20men%20for%20holy%20days%2C--all%20are%20here.%20No%20wonder%20that%20men%20look%20back%20upon%20their%20college%20life%20as%20upon%20halcyon%20days%2C%20the%20romantic%20period%20of%20youth.%20No%20wonder%20that%20Dr.%20Holmes%26%2339%3Bs%20poems%20to%20his%20Harvard%20classmates%20find%20an%20echo%20in%20college%20reunions%20everywhere%3B%20and%20gray-haired%20men%2C%20who%20outside%20the%20narrowing%20circle%20of%20home%20have%20not%20heard%20their%20first%20names%20for%20years%2C%20remain%20Bill%20and%20Joe%20and%20John%20and%20George%20to%20college%20comrades%2C%20even%20if%20unseen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20generation.%20Yet%20a%20girl%20should%20go%20to%20college%20not%20merely%20to%20obtain%20four%20happy%20years%20but%20to%20make%20a%20second%20gain%2C%20which%20is%20often%20overlooked%2C%20and%20is%20little%20understood%20even%20when%20perceived%3B%20I%20mean%20a%20gain%20in%20health.%20The%20old%20notion%20that%20low%20vitality%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20course%20with%20women%3B%20that%20to%20be%20delicate%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20superior%20refinement%2C%20especially%20in%20well-to-do%20families%3B%20that%20sickness%20is%20a%20dispensation%20of%20Providence%2C--these%20notions%20meet%20with%20no%20acceptance%20in%20college.%20Years%20ago%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20mirror%20frame%20of%20a%20college%20freshman%26%2339%3Bs%20room%20this%20little%20formula%3A%20%22Sickness%20is%20carelessness%2C%20carelessness%20is%20selfishness%2C%20and%20selfishness%20is%20sin.%22%20And%20I%20have%20often%20noticed%20among%20college%20girls%20an%20air%20of%20humiliation%20and%20shame%20when%20obliged%20to%20confess%20a%20lack%20of%20physical%20vigor%2C%20as%20if%20they%20were%20convicted%20of%20managing%20life%20with%20bad%20judgment%2C%20or%20of%20some%20moral%20delinquency.%20With%20the%20spreading%20scientific%20conviction%20that%20health%20is%20a%20matter%20largely%20under%20each%20person%26%2339%3Bs%20control%2C%20that%20even%20inherited%20tendencies%20to%20disease%20need%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20run%20their%20riotous%20course%20unchecked%2C%20there%20comes%20an%20earnest%20purpose%20to%20be%20strong%20and%20free.%20Fascinating%20fields%20of%20knowledge%20are%20waiting%20to%20be%20explored%3B%20possibilities%20of%20doing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20knowing%2C%20are%20on%20every%20side%3B%20new%20and%20dear%20friendships%20enlarge%20and%20sweeten%20dreams%20of%20future%20study%20and%20work%2C%20and%20the%20young%20student%20cannot%20afford%20quivering%20nerves%20or%20small%20lungs%20or%20an%20aching%20head%20any%20more%20than%20bad%20taste%2C%20rough%20manners%2C%20or%20a%20weak%20will.%20Handicapped%20by%20inheritance%20or%20bad%20training%2C%20she%20finds%20the%20plan%20of%20college%20life%20itself%20her%20supporter%20and%20friend.%20The%20steady%2C%20long-continued%20routine%20of%20mental%20work%2C%20physical%20exercise%2C%20recreation%2C%20and%20sleep%2C%20the%20simple%20and%20wholesome%20food%2C%20in%20place%20of%20irregular%20and%20unstudied%20diet%2C%20work%20out%20salvation%20for%20her.%20Instead%20of%20being%20left%20to%20go%20out-of-doors%20when%20she%20feels%20like%20it%2C%20the%20regular%20training%20of%20the%20gymnasium%2C%20the%20boats%20on%20lake%20and%20river%2C%20the%20tennis%20court%2C%20the%20golf%20links%2C%20the%20basket%20ball%2C%20the%20bicycle%2C%20the%20long%20walk%20among%20the%20woods%20in%20search%20of%20botanical%20or%20geological%20specimens%2C--all%20these%20and%20many%20more%20call%20to%20the%20busy%20student%2C%20until%20she%20realizes%20that%20they%20have%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20every%20well-ordered%20day%20of%20every%20month.%20So%20she%20learns%2C%20little%20by%20little%2C%20that%20buoyant%20health%20is%20a%20precious%20possession%20to%20be%20won%20and%20kept.%20It%20is%20significant%20that%20already%20statistical%20investigation%20in%20this%20country%20and%20in%20England%20shows%20that%20the%20standard%20of%20health%20is%20higher%20among%20the%20women%20who%20hold%20college%20degrees%20than%20among%20any%20other%20equal%20number%20of%20the%20same%20age%20and%20class.%20And%20it%20is%20interesting%20also%20to%20observe%20to%20what%20sort%20of%20questions%20our%20recent%20girl%20graduates%20have%20been%20inclined%20to%20devote%20attention.%20They%20have%20been%20largely%20the%20neglected%20problems%20of%20little%20children%20and%20their%20health%2C%20of%20home%20sanitation%2C%20of%20food%20and%20its%20choice%20and%20preparation%2C%20of%20domestic%20service%2C%20of%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20schools%20and%20public%20buildings.%20Colleges%20for%20girls%20are%20pledged%20by%20their%20very%20constitution%20to%20make%20persistent%20war%20on%20the%20water%20cure%2C%20the%20nervine%20retreat%2C%20the%20insane%20asylum%2C%20the%20hospital%2C--those%20bitter%20fruits%20of%20the%20emotional%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20women.%20%22I%20can%20never%20afford%20a%20sick%20headache%20again%2C%20life%20is%20so%20interesting%20and%20there%20is%20so%20much%20to%20do%2C%22%20a%20delicate%20girl%20said%20to%20me%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20college%20year.%20And%20while%20her%20mother%20was%20in%20a%20far-off%20invalid%20retreat%2C%20she%20undertook%20the%20battle%20against%20fate%20with%20the%20same%20intelligence%20and%20courage%20which%20she%20put%20into%20her%20calculus%20problems%20and%20her%20translations%20of%20Sophocles.%20Her%20beautiful%20home%20and%20her%20rosy%20and%20happy%20children%20prove%20the%20measure%20of%20her%20hard-won%20success.%20Formerly%20the%20majority%20of%20physicians%20had%20but%20one%20question%20for%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20nervous%20and%20delicate%20girl%2C%20%22Does%20she%20go%20to%20school%3F%22%20And%20only%20one%20prescription%2C%20%22Take%20her%20out%20of%20school.%22%20Never%20a%20suggestion%20as%20to%20suppers%20of%20pickles%20and%20pound-cake%2C%20never%20a%20hint%20about%20midnight%20dancing%20and%20hurried%20day-time%20ways.%20But%20now%20the%20sensible%20doctor%20asks%2C%20%22What%20are%20her%20interests%3F%20What%20are%20her%20tastes%3F%20What%20are%20her%20habits%3F%22%20And%20he%20finds%20new%20interests%20for%20her%2C%20and%20urges%20the%20formation%20of%20out-of-door%20tastes%20and%20steady%20occupation%20for%20the%20mind%2C%20in%20order%20to%20draw%20the%20morbid%20girl%20from%20herself%20into%20the%20invigorating%20world%20outside.%20This%20the%20college%20does%20largely%20through%20its%20third%20gift%20of%20friendship.%20Until%20a%20girl%20goes%20away%20from%20home%20to%20school%20or%20college%2C%20her%20friends%20are%20chiefly%20chosen%20for%20her%20by%20circumstances.%20Her%20young%20relatives%2C%20her%20neighbors%20in%20the%20same%20street%2C%20those%20who%20happen%20to%20go%20to%20the%20same%20school%20or%20church%2C--these%20she%20makes%20her%20girlish%20intimates.%20She%20goes%20to%20college%20with%20the%20entire%20conviction%2C%20half%20unknown%20to%20herself%2C%20that%20her%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20political%20party%20contains%20all%20the%20honest%20men%2C%20her%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20circle%20all%20the%20true%20ladies%2C%20her%20church%20all%20the%20real%20saints%20of%20the%20community.%20And%20the%20smaller%20the%20town%2C%20the%20more%20absolute%20is%20her%20belief.%20But%20in%20college%20she%20finds%20that%20the%20girl%20who%20earned%20her%20scholarship%20in%20the%20village%20school%20sits%20beside%20the%20banker%26%2339%3Bs%20daughter%3B%20the%20New%20England%20farmer%26%2339%3Bs%20child%20rooms%20next%20the%20heiress%20of%20a%20Hawaiian%20sugar%20plantation%3B%20the%20daughters%20of%20the%20opposing%20candidates%20in%20a%20sharply%20fought%20election%20have%20grown%20great%20friends%20in%20college%20boats%20and%20laboratories%3B%20and%20before%20her%20diploma%20is%20won%20she%20realizes%20how%20much%20richer%20a%20world%20she%20lives%20in%20than%20she%20ever%20dreamed%20of%20at%20home.%20The%20wealth%20that%20lies%20in%20differences%20has%20dawned%20upon%20her%20vision.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%20sit%20down%20together%20that%20either%20can%20understand%20how%20the%20Lord%20is%20the%20Maker%20of%20them%20all.%20To-day%20above%20all%20things%20we%20need%20the%20influence%20of%20men%20and%20women%20of%20friendliness%2C%20of%20generous%20nature%2C%20of%20hospitality%20to%20new%20ideas%2C%20in%20short%2C%20of%20social%20imagination.%20But%20instead%2C%20we%20find%20each%20political%20party%20bitterly%20calling%20the%20other%20dishonest%2C%20each%20class%20suspicious%20of%20the%20intentions%20of%20the%20other%2C%20and%20in%20social%20life%20the%20pettiest%20standards%20of%20conduct.%20Is%20it%20not%20well%20for%20us%20that%20the%20colleges%20all%20over%20the%20country%20still%20offer%20to%20their%20fortunate%20students%20a%20society%20of%20the%20most%20democratic%20sort%2C--one%20in%20which%20a%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20money%2C%20a%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20position%2C%20can%20assure%20no%20distinction%20and%20make%20no%20close%20friends%3F%20Here%20capacity%20of%20every%20kind%20counts%20for%20its%20full%20value.%20Here%20enthusiasm%20waits%20to%20make%20heroes%20of%20those%20who%20can%20lead.%20Here%20charming%20manners%2C%20noble%20character%2C%20amiable%20temper%2C%20scholarly%20power%2C%20find%20their%20full%20opportunity%20and%20inspire%20such%20friendships%20as%20are%20seldom%20made%20afterward.%20I%20have%20forgotten%20my%20chemistry%2C%20and%20my%20classical%20philology%20cannot%20bear%20examination%3B%20but%20all%20round%20the%20world%20there%20are%20men%20and%20women%20at%20work%2C%20my%20intimates%20of%20college%20days%2C%20who%20have%20made%20the%20wide%20earth%20a%20friendly%20place%20to%20me.%20Of%20every%20creed%2C%20of%20every%20party%2C%20in%20far-away%20places%20and%20in%20near%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20them%20makes%20me%20more%20courageous%20in%20duty%20and%20more%20faithful%20to%20opportunity%2C%20though%20for%20many%20years%20we%20may%20not%20have%20had%20time%20to%20write%20each%20other%20a%20letter.%20The%20basis%20of%20all%20valuable%20and%20enduring%20friendships%20is%20not%20accident%20or%20juxtaposition%2C%20but%20tastes%2C%20interests%2C%20habits%2C%20work%2C%20ambitions.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20to%20college%20friendship%20clings%20a%20romance%20entirely%20its%20own.%20One%20of%20the%20friends%20may%20spend%20her%20days%20in%20the%20laboratory%2C%20eagerly%20chasing%20the%20shy%20facts%20that%20hide%20beyond%20the%20microscope%26%2339%3Bs%20fine%20vision%2C%20and%20the%20other%20may%20fill%20her%20hours%20and%20her%20heart%20with%20the%20poets%20and%20the%20philosophers%3B%20one%20may%20steadfastly%20pursue%20her%20way%20toward%20the%20command%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20other%20towards%20the%20world%20of%20letters%20and%20of%20art%3B%20these%20divergences%20constitute%20no%20barrier%2C%20but%20rather%20an%20aid%20to%20the%20fulness%20of%20friendship.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20goes%20in%20a%20simple%20gown%20which%20she%20has%20earned%20and%20made%20herself%2C%20and%20the%20other%20lives%20when%20at%20home%20in%20a%20merchant%26%2339%3Bs%20modern%20palace--what%20has%20that%20to%20do%20with%20the%20things%20the%20girls%20care%20about%20and%20the%20dreams%20they%20talk%20over%20in%20the%20walk%20by%20the%20river%20or%20the%20bicycle%20ride%20through%20country%20roads%3F%20If%20any%20young%20man%20to-day%20goes%20through%20Harvard%20lonely%2C%20neglected%2C%20unfriended%2C%20if%20any%20girl%20lives%20solitary%20and%20wretched%20in%20her%20life%20at%20Wellesley%2C%20it%20is%20their%20own%20fault.%20It%20must%20be%20because%20they%20are%20suspicious%2C%20unfriendly%20or%20disagreeable%20themselves.%20Certainly%20it%20is%20true%20that%20in%20the%20associations%20of%20college%20life%2C%20more%20than%20in%20any%20other%20that%20the%20country%20can%20show%2C%20what%20is%20extraneous%2C%20artificial%2C%20and%20temporary%20falls%20away%2C%20and%20the%20every-day%20relations%20of%20life%20and%20work%20take%20on%20a%20character%20that%20is%20simple%2C%20natural%2C%20genuine.%20And%20so%20it%20comes%20about%20that%20the%20fourth%20gift%20of%20college%20life%20is%20ideals%20of%20personal%20character.%20To%20some%20people%20the%20shaping%20ideals%20of%20what%20character%20should%20be%2C%20often%20held%20unconsciously%2C%20come%20from%20the%20books%20they%20are%20given%20by%20the%20persons%20whom%20they%20most%20admire%20before%20they%20are%20twenty%20years%20old.%20The%20greatest%20thing%20any%20friend%20or%20teacher%2C%20either%20in%20school%20or%20college%2C%20can%20do%20for%20a%20student%20is%20to%20furnish%20him%20with%20a%20personal%20ideal.%20The%20college%20professors%20who%20transformed%20me%20through%20my%20acquaintance%20with%20them--ah%2C%20they%20were%20few%2C%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20dozen%20conversations%20with%20them%20outside%20their%20class%20rooms--gave%20me%2C%20each%20in%20his%20different%20way%2C%20an%20ideal%20of%20character%2C%20of%20conduct%2C%20of%20the%20scholar%2C%20the%20leader%2C%20of%20which%20they%20and%20I%20were%20totally%20unconscious%20at%20the%20time.%20For%20many%20years%20I%20have%20known%20that%20my%20study%20with%20them%2C%20no%20matter%20whether%20of%20philosophy%20or%20of%20Greek%2C%20of%20mathematics%20or%20history%20or%20English%2C%20enlarged%20my%20notions%20of%20life%2C%20uplifted%20my%20standards%20of%20culture%2C%20and%20so%20inspired%20me%20with%20new%20possibilities%20of%20usefulness%20and%20of%20happiness.%20Not%20the%20facts%20and%20theories%20that%20I%20learned%20so%20much%20as%20the%20men%20who%20taught%20me%2C%20gave%20this%20inspiration.%20The%20community%20at%20large%20is%20right%20in%20saying%20that%20it%20wants%20the%20personal%20influence%20of%20professors%20on%20students%2C%20but%20it%20is%20wholly%20wrong%20in%20assuming%20that%20this%20precious%20influence%20comes%20from%20frequent%20meetings%20or%20talks%20on%20miscellaneous%20subjects.%20There%20is%20quite%20as%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20quickening%20force%20in%20the%20somewhat%20remote%20and%20mysterious%20power%20of%20the%20teacher%20who%20devotes%20himself%20to%20amassing%20treasures%20of%20scholarship%2C%20or%20to%20patiently%20working%20out%20the%20best%20methods%20of%20teaching%3B%20who%20standing%20somewhat%20apart%2C%20still%20remains%20an%20ideal%20of%20the%20Christian%20scholar%2C%20the%20just%2C%20the%20courteous%20man%20or%20woman.%20To%20come%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20one%20such%20teacher%20is%20enough%20to%20make%20college%20life%20worthwhile.%20A%20young%20man%20who%20came%20to%20Harvard%20with%20eighty%20cents%20in%20his%20pocket%2C%20and%20worked%20his%20way%20through%2C%20never%20a%20high%20scholar%2C%20and%20now%20in%20a%20business%20which%20looks%20very%20commonplace%2C%20told%20me%20the%20other%20day%20that%20he%20would%20not%20care%20to%20be%20alive%20if%20he%20had%20not%20gone%20to%20college.%20His%20face%20flushed%20as%20he%20explained%20how%20different%20his%20days%20would%20have%20been%20if%20he%20had%20not%20known%20two%20of%20his%20professors.%20%22Do%20you%20use%20your%20college%20studies%20in%20your%20business%3F%22%20I%20asked.%20%22Oh%2C%20no!%22%20he%20answered.%20%22But%20I%20am%20another%20man%20in%20doing%20the%20business%3B%20and%20when%20the%20day%26%2339%3Bs%20work%20is%20done%20I%20live%20another%20life%20because%20of%20my%20college%20experiences.%20The%20business%20and%20I%20are%20both%20the%20better%20for%20it%20every%20day.%22%20How%20many%20a%20young%20girl%20has%20had%20her%20whole%20horizon%20extended%20by%20the%20changed%20ideals%20she%20gained%20in%20college!%20Yet%20this%20is%20largely%20because%20the%20associations%20and%20studies%20there%20are%20likely%20to%20give%20her%20permanent%20interests--the%20fifth%20and%20perhaps%20the%20greatest%20gift%20of%20college%20life%20of%20which%20I%20shall%20speak.%20The%20old