going%20slumming%20among%20the%20Italians.%20I%20have%20too%20much%20respect%20for%20the%20Italians.%20And%20what%20shall%20I%20do%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%3F%22%20That%20was%20a%20frank%20statement%20of%20what%20any%20girl%20of%20brains%20or%20conscience%20feels%2C%20with%20more%20or%20less%20bitter%20distinctness%2C%20unless%20she%20marries%20early%2C%20or%20has%20some%20pressing%20work%20for%20which%20she%20is%20well%20trained.%20Yet%20even%20if%20that%20which%20is%20the%20profession%20of%20woman%20par%20excellence%20be%20hers%2C%20how%20can%20she%20be%20perennially%20so%20interesting%20a%20companion%20to%20her%20husband%20and%20children%20as%20if%20she%20had%20keen%20personal%20tastes%2C%20long%20her%20own%2C%20and%20growing%20with%20her%20growth%3F%20Indeed%2C%20in%20that%20respect%20the%20condition%20of%20men%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20women.%20It%20would%20be%20quite%20the%20same%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20man%26%2339%3Bs%20business%20or%20profession%20is%20generally%20in%20itself%20a%20means%20of%20growth%2C%20of%20education%2C%20of%20dignity.%20He%20leans%20his%20life%20against%20it.%20He%20builds%20his%20home%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20it.%20It%20binds%20his%20days%20together%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20natural%20piety%20and%20makes%20him%20advance%20in%20strength%20and%20nobility%20as%20he%20%22fulfils%20the%20common%20round%2C%20the%20daily%20task.%22%20And%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20men%20in%20the%20past%2C%20if%20they%20have%20been%20honorable%20men%2C%20have%20grown%20old%20better%20than%20women.%20Men%20usually%20retain%20their%20ability%20longer%2C%20their%20mental%20alertness%20and%20hospitality.%20They%20add%20fine%20quality%20to%20fine%20quality%2C%20passing%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20preserving%20in%20old%20age%20whatever%20has%20been%20best%20in%20youth.%20It%20was%20a%20sudden%20recognition%20of%20this%20fact%20which%20made%20a%20young%20friend%20of%20mine%20say%20last%20winter%2C%20%22I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20parties%20any%20more%3B%20the%20men%20best%20worth%20talking%20with%20are%20too%20old%20to%20dance.%22%20Even%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20permanent%20business%20or%20profession%2C%20however%2C%20the%20most%20interesting%20men%20I%20know%20are%20those%20who%20have%20an%20avocation%20as%20well%20as%20a%20vocation.%20I%20mean%20a%20taste%20or%20work%20quite%20apart%20from%20the%20business%20of%20life.%20This%20revives%2C%20inspires%2C%20and%20cultivates%20them%20perpetually.%20It%20matters%20little%20what%20it%20is%2C%20if%20only%20it%20is%20real%20and%20personal%2C%20is%20large%20enough%20to%20last%2C%20and%20possesses%20the%20power%20of%20growth.%20A%20young%20sea-captain%20from%20a%20New%20England%20village%20on%20a%20long%20and%20lonely%20voyage%20falls%20upon%20a%20copy%20of%20Shelley.%20Appeal%20is%20made%20to%20his%20fine%20but%20untrained%20mind%2C%20and%20the%20book%20of%20the%20boy%20poet%20becomes%20the%20seaman%26%2339%3Bs%20university.%20The%20wide%20world%20of%20poetry%20and%20of%20the%20other%20fine%20arts%20is%20opened%2C%20and%20the%20Shelleyian%20specialist%20becomes%20a%20cultivated%2C%20original%2C%20and%20charming%20man.%20A%20busy%20merchant%20loves%20flowers%2C%20and%20in%20all%20his%20free%20hours%20studies%20them.%20Each%20new%20spring%20adds%20knowledge%20to%20his%20knowledge%2C%20and%20his%20friends%20continually%20bring%20him%20their%20strange%20discoveries.%20With%20growing%20wealth%20he%20cultivates%20rare%20and%20beautiful%20plants%2C%20and%20shares%20them%20with%20his%20fortunate%20acquaintances.%20Happy%20the%20companion%20invited%20to%20a%20walk%20or%20a%20drive%20with%20such%20observant%20eyes%2C%20such%20vivid%20talk!%20Because%20of%20this%20cheerful%20interest%20in%20flowers%2C%20and%20this%20ingenious%20skill%20in%20dealing%20with%20them%2C%20the%20man%20himself%20is%20interesting.%20All%20his%20powers%20are%20alert%2C%20and%20his%20judgment%20is%20valued%20in%20public%20life%20and%20in%20private%20business.%20Or%20is%20it%20more%20exact%20to%20say%20that%20because%20he%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20man%20who%20would%20insist%20upon%20having%20such%20interests%20outside%20his%20daily%20work%2C%20he%20is%20still%20fresh%20and%20young%20and%20capable%20of%20growth%20at%20an%20age%20when%20many%20other%20men%20are%20dull%20and%20old%20and%20certain%20that%20the%20time%20of%20decay%20is%20at%20hand%3F%20There%20are%20two%20reasons%20why%20women%20need%20to%20cultivate%20these%20large%20and%20abiding%20interests%20even%20more%20persistently%20than%20men.%20In%20the%20first%20place%2C%20they%20have%20more%20leisure.%20They%20are%20indeed%20the%20only%20leisure%20class%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20only%20large%20body%20of%20persons%20who%20are%20not%20called%20upon%20to%20win%20their%20daily%20bread%20in%20direct%20wage-earning%20ways.%20As%20yet%2C%20fortunately%2C%20few%20men%20among%20us%20have%20so%20little%20self-respect%20as%20to%20idle%20about%20our%20streets%20and%20drawing-rooms%20because%20their%20fathers%20are%20rich%20enough%20to%20support%20them.%20We%20are%20not%20without%20our%20unemployed%20poor%3B%20but%20roving%20tramps%20and%20idle%20clubmen%20are%20after%20all%20not%20of%20large%20consequence.%20Our%20serious%2C%20non-producing%20classes%20are%20chiefly%20women.%20It%20is%20the%20regular%20ambition%20of%20the%20chivalrous%20American%20to%20make%20all%20the%20women%20who%20depend%20on%20him%20so%20comfortable%20that%20they%20need%20do%20nothing%20for%20themselves.%20Machinery%20has%20taken%20nearly%20all%20the%20former%20occupations%20of%20women%20out%20of%20the%20home%20into%20the%20shop%20and%20factory.%20Widespread%20wealth%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20the%20inherited%20theory%20that%20it%20is%20not%20well%20for%20the%20woman%20to%20earn%20money%20so%20long%20as%20father%20or%20brothers%20can%20support%20her%2C%20have%20brought%20about%20a%20condition%20of%20things%20in%20which%20there%20is%20social%20danger%2C%20unless%20with%20the%20larger%20leisure%20are%20given%20high%20and%20enduring%20interests.%20To%20health%20especially%20there%20is%20great%20danger%2C%20for%20nothing%20breaks%20down%20a%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20health%20like%20idleness%20and%20its%20resulting%20ennui.%20More%20people%2C%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20are%20broken%20down%20nervously%20because%20they%20are%20bored%2C%20than%20because%20they%20are%20overworked%3B%20and%20more%20still%20go%20to%20pieces%20through%20fussiness%2C%20unwholesome%20living%2C%20worry%20over%20petty%20details%2C%20and%20the%20daily%20disappointments%20which%20result%20from%20small%20and%20superficial%20training.%20And%20then%2C%20besides%20the%20danger%20to%20health%2C%20there%20is%20the%20danger%20to%20character.%20I%20need%20not%20dwell%20on%20the%20undermining%20influence%20which%20men%20also%20feel%20when%20occupation%20is%20taken%20away%20and%20no%20absorbing%20private%20interest%20fills%20the%20vacancy.%20The%20vices%20of%20luxurious%20city%20life%20are%20perhaps%20hardly%20more%20destructive%20to%20character%20than%20is%20the%20slow%20deterioration%20of%20barren%20country%20life.%20Though%20the%20conditions%20in%20the%20two%20cases%20are%20exactly%20opposite%2C%20the%20trouble%20is%20often%20the%20same%2C--absence%20of%20noble%20interests.%20In%20the%20city%20restless%20idleness%20organizes%20amusement%3B%20in%20the%20country%20deadly%20dulness%20succeeds%20daily%20toil.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20second%20reason%20why%20a%20girl%20should%20acquire%20for%20herself%20strong%20and%20worthy%20interests.%20The%20regular%20occupations%20of%20women%20in%20their%20homes%20are%20generally%20disconnected%20and%20of%20little%20educational%20value%2C%20at%20least%20as%20those%20homes%20are%20at%20present%20conducted.%20Given%20the%20best%20will%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20daily%20doing%20of%20household%20details%20becomes%20a%20wearisome%20monotony%20if%20the%20mere%20performance%20of%20them%20is%20all.%20To%20make%20drudgery%20divine%20a%20woman%20must%20have%20a%20brain%20to%20plan%20and%20eyes%20to%20see%20how%20to%20%22sweep%20a%20room%20as%20to%20God%26%2339%3Bs%20laws.%22%20Imagination%20and%20knowledge%20should%20be%20the%20hourly%20companions%20of%20her%20who%20would%20make%20a%20fine%20art%20of%20each%20detail%20in%20kitchen%20and%20nursery.%20Too%20long%20has%20the%20pin%20been%20the%20appropriate%20symbol%20of%20the%20average%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20life--the%20pin%2C%20which%20only%20temporarily%20holds%20together%20things%20which%20may%20or%20may%20not%20have%20any%20organic%20connection%20with%20one%20another.%20While%20undoubtedly%20most%20women%20must%20spend%20the%20larger%20part%20of%20life%20in%20this%20modest%20pin-work%2C%20holding%20together%20the%20little%20things%20of%20home%20and%20school%20and%20society%20and%20church%2C%20it%20is%20also%20true%2C%20that%20cohesive%20work%20itself%20cannot%20be%20done%20well%2C%20even%20in%20humble%20circumstances%2C%20except%20by%20the%20refined%2C%20the%20trained%2C%20the%20growing%20woman.%20The%20smallest%20village%2C%20the%20plainest%20home%2C%20give%20ample%20space%20for%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20trained%20college%20woman.%20And%20the%20reason%20why%20such%20homes%20and%20such%20villages%20are%20so%20often%20barren%20of%20grace%20and%20variety%20is%20just%20because%20these%20fine%20qualities%20have%20not%20ruled%20them.%20The%20higher%20graces%20of%20civilization%20halt%20among%20us%3B%20dainty%20and%20finished%20ways%20of%20living%20give%20place%20to%20common%20ways%2C%20while%20vulgar%20tastes%2C%20slatternly%20habits%2C%20clouds%20and%20despondency%20reign%20in%20the%20house.%20Little%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20die%20in%20needless%20thousands%20because%20of%20the%20dull%2C%20unimaginative%20women%20on%20whom%20they%20depend.%20Such%20women%20have%20been%20satisfied%20with%20just%20getting%20along%2C%20instead%20of%20packing%20everything%20they%20do%20with%20brains%2C%20instead%20of%20studying%20the%20best%20possible%20way%20of%20doing%20everything%20small%20or%20large%3B%20for%20there%20is%20always%20a%20best%20way%2C%20whether%20of%20setting%20a%20table%2C%20of%20trimming%20a%20hat%2C%20or%20teaching%20a%20child%20to%20read.%20And%20this%20taste%20for%20perfection%20can%20be%20cultivated%3B%20indeed%2C%20it%20must%20be%20cultivated%2C%20if%20our%20standards%20of%20living%20are%20to%20be%20raised.%20There%20is%20now%20scientific%20knowledge%20enough%2C%20there%20is%20money%20enough%2C%20to%20prevent%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20evils%20which%20afflict%20our%20social%20organism%2C%20if%20mere%20knowledge%20or%20wealth%20could%20avail%3B%20but%20the%20greater%20difficulty%20is%20to%20make%20intelligence%2C%20character%2C%20good%20taste%2C%20unselfishness%20prevail.%20What%2C%20then%2C%20are%20the%20interests%20which%20powerfully%20appeal%20to%20mind%20and%20heart%2C%20and%20so%20are%20fitted%20to%20become%20the%20strengthening%20companions%20of%20a%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20life%3F%20I%20shall%20mention%20only%20three%2C%20all%20of%20them%20such%20as%20are%20elaborately%20fostered%20by%20college%20life.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20love%20of%20great%20literature.%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20that%20use%20of%20books%20by%20which%20a%20man%20may%20get%20what%20is%20called%20a%20good%20education%20and%20so%20be%20better%20qualified%20for%20the%20battle%20of%20life%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20mention%20books%20in%20their%20character%20as%20reservoirs%20of%20knowledge%2C%20books%20which%20we%20need%20for%20special%20purposes%2C%20and%20which%20are%20no%20longer%20of%20consequence%20when%20our%20purpose%20with%20them%20is%20served.%20I%20have%20in%20mind%20the%20great%20books%2C%20especially%20the%20great%20poets%2C%20books%20to%20be%20adopted%20as%20a%20resource%20and%20a%20solace.%20The%20chief%20reason%20why%20so%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20how%20to%20make%20comrades%20of%20such%20books%20is%20because%20they%20have%20come%20to%20them%20too%20late.%20We%20have%20in%20this%20country%20enormous%20numbers%20of%20readers%2C%20probably%20a%20larger%20number%20who%20read%2C%20and%20who%20read%20many%20hours%20in%20the%20week%2C%20than%20has%20ever%20been%20known%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20what%20do%20these%20millions%20read%20besides%20the%20newspapers%3F%20Possibly%20a%20denominational%20religious%20weekly%20and%20another%20journal%20of%20fashion%20or%20business.%20Then%20come%20the%20thousands%20who%20read%20the%20best%20magazines%2C%20and%20whatever%20else%20is%20for%20the%20moment%20popular%20in%20novels%20and%20poetry--the%20last%20dialect%20story%2C%20the%20fashionable%20poem%2C%20the%20questionable%20but%20talked-of%20novel.%20Let%20a%20violent%20attack%20be%20made%20on%20the%20decency%20of%20a%20new%20story%20and%20instantly%2C%20if%20only%20it%20is%20clever%2C%20its%20author%20becomes%20famous.%20But%20the%20fashions%20in%20reading%20of%20a%20restless%20race--the%20women%20too%20idle%2C%20the%20men%20too%20heavily%20worked--I%20will%20not%20discuss%20here.%20Let%20light%20literature%20be%20devourered%20by%20our%20populace%20as%20his%20drug%20is%20taken%20by%20the%20opium-eater%2C%20and%20with%20a%20similar%20narcotic%20effect.%20We%20can%20only%20seek%20out%20the%20children%2C%20and%20hope%20by%20giving%20them%20from%20babyhood%20bits%20of%20the%20noblest%20literature%2C%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20great%20opportunities%20of%20mature%20life.%20I%20urge%2C%20therefore%2C%20reading%20as%20a%20mental%20stimulus%2C%20as%20a%20solace%20in%20trouble%2C%20a%20perpetual%20source%20of%20delight%3B%20and%20I%20would%20point%20out%20that%20we%20must%20not%20delay%20to%20make%20the%20great%20friendships%20that%20await%20us%20on%20the%20library%20shelves%20until%20sickness%20shuts%20the%20door%20on%20the%20outer%20world%2C%20or%20death%20enters%20the%20home%20and%20silences%20the%20voices%20that%20once%20helped%20to%20make%20these%20friendships%20sweet.%20If%20Homer%20and%20Shakespeare%20and%20Wordsworth%20and%20Browning%20are%20to%20have%20meaning%20for%20us%20when%20we%20need%20them%20most%2C%20it%20will%20be%20because%20they%20come%20to%20us%20as%20old%20familiar%20friends%20whose%20influences%20have%20permeated%20the%20glad%20and%20busy%20days%20before.%20The%20last%20time%20I%20heard%20James%20Russell%20Lowell%20talk%20to%20college%20girls%2C%20he%20said%2C--for%20he%20was%20too%20ill%20to%20say%20many%20words--%22I%20have%20only%20this%20one%20message%20to%20leave%20with%20you.%20In%20all%20your%20work%20in%20college%20never%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20you%20have%20come%20here.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20you%20may%20get%20something%20by%20which%20to%20earn%20your%20bread%2C%20but%20that%20every%20mouthful%20of%20bread%20may%20be%20the%20sweeter%20to%20your%20taste.%22%20And%20this%20is%20the%20power%20possessed%20by%20the%20mighty%20dead%2C--men%20of%20every%20time%20and%20nation%2C%20whose%20voices%20death%20cannot%20silence%2C%20who%20are%20waiting%20even%20at%20the%20poor%20man%26%2339%3Bs%20elbow%2C%20whose%20illuminating%20words%20may%20be%20had%20for%20the%20price%20of%20a%20day%26%2339%3Bs%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen%20or%20the%20street%2C%20for%20lack%20of%20love%20of%20whom%20many%20a%20luxurious%20home%20is%20a%20dull%20and%20solitary%20spot%2C%20breeding%20misery%20and%20vice.%20Now%20the%20modern%20college%20is%20especially%20equipped%20to%20introduce%20its%20students%20to%20such%20literature.%20The%20library%20is%20at%20last%20understood%20to%20be%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20college.%20The%20modern%20librarian%20is%20not%20the%20keeper%20of%20books%2C%20as%20was%20his%20predecessor%2C%20but%20the%20distributer%20of%20them%2C%20and%20the%20guide%20to%20their%20resources%2C%20proud%20when%20he%20increases%20the%20use%20of%20his%20treasures.%20Every%20language%2C%20ancient%20or%20modern%2C%20which%20contains%20a%20literature%20is%20now%20taught%20in%20college.%20Its%20history%20is%20examined%2C%20its%20philology%2C%20its%20masterpieces%2C%20and%20more%20than%20ever%20is%20English%20literature%20studied%20and%20loved.%20There%20is%20now%20every%20opportunity%20for%20the%20college%20student%20to%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20use%20of%20his%20own%20tongue%20and%20pen.%20What%20other%20men%20painfully%20strive%20for%20he%20can%20enjoy%20to%20the%20full%20with%20comparatively%20little%20effort.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20second%20invigorating%20interest%20to%20which%20college%20training%20introduces%20its%20student.%20I%20mean%20the%20study%20of%20nature%2C%20intimacy%20with%20the%20strange%20and%20beautiful%20world%20in%20which%20we%20live.%20%22Nature%20never%20did%20betray%20the%20heart%20that%20loved%20her%2C%22%20sang%20her%20poet%20high%20priest.%20When%20the%20world%20has%20been%20too%20much%20with%20us%2C%20nothing%20else%20is%20so%20refreshing%20to%20tired%20eyes%20and%20mind%20as%20woods%20and%20water%2C%20and%20an%20intelligent%20knowledge%20of%20the%20life%20within%20them.%20For%20a%20generation%20past%20there%20has%20been%20a%20well-nigh%20universal%20turning%20of%20the%20population%20toward%20the%20cities.%20In%201840%20only%20nine%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20people%20lived%20in%20cities%20of%208%2C000%20inhabitants%20or%20more.%20Now%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20us%20are%20found%20in%20cities.%20But%20the%20electric-car%2C%20the%20telephone%2C%20the%20bicycle%2C%20still%20keep%20avenues%20to%20the%20country%20open.%20Certain%20it%20is%20that%20city%20people%20feel%20a%20growing%20hunger%20for%20the%20country%2C%20particularly%20when%20grass%20begins%20to%20grow.%20This%20is%20a%20healthy%20taste%2C%20and%20must%20increase%20the%20general%20knowledge%20and%20love%20of%20nature.%20Fortunate%20are%20the%20little%20children%20in%20those%20schools%20whose%20teachers%20know%20and%20love%20the%20world%20in%20which%20they%20live.%20Their%20young%20eyes%20are%20early%20opened%20to%20the%20beauty%20of%20birds%20and%20trees%20and%20plants.%20Not%20only%20should%20we%20expect%20our%20girls%20to%20have%20a%20feeling%20for%20the%20fine%20sunset%20or%20the%20wide-reaching%20panorama%20of%20field%20and%20water%2C%20but%20to%20know%20something%20also%20about%20the%20less%20obvious%20aspects%20of%20nature%2C%20its%20structure%2C%20its%20methods%20of%20work%2C%20and%20the%20endless%20diversity%20of%20its%20parts.%20No%20one%20can%20have%20read%20Matthew%20Arnold%26%2339%3Bs%20letters%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20his%20sister%2C%20without%20being%20struck%20by%20the%20immense%20enjoyment%20he%20took%20throughout%20his%20singularly%20simple%20and%20hard-working%20life%20in%20flowers%20and%20trees%20and%20rivers.%20The%20English%20lake%20country%20had%20given%20him%20this%20happy%20inheritance%2C%20with%20everywhere%20its%20sound%20of%20running%20water%20and%20its%20wealth%20of%20greenery.%20There%20is%20a%20close%20connection%20between%20the%20marvellous%20unbroken%20line%20of%20English%20song%2C%20and%20the%20passionate%20love%20of%20the%20Englishman%20for%20a%20home%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20birds%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20green%20fields.%20%22The%20world%20is%20so%20full%20of%20a%20number%20of%20things%2C%20That%20I%20think%20we%20should%20all%20be%20as%20happy%20as%20kings%2C%22%20is%20the%20opinion%20of%20everybody%20who%20knows%20nature%20as%20did%20Robert%20Louis%20Stevenson.%20And%20so%20our%20college%20student%20may%20begin%20to%20know%20it.%20Let%20her%20enter%20the%20laboratories%20and%20investigate%20for%20herself.%20Let%20her%20make%20her%20delicate%20experiments%20with%20the%20blowpipe%20or%20the%20balance%3B%20let%20her%20track%20mysterious%20life%20from%20one%20hiding-place%20to%20another%3B%20let%20her%20%22name%20all%20the%20birds%20without%20a%20gun%2C%22%20and%20make%20intimates%20of%20flower%20and%20fish%20and%20butterfly--and%20she%20is%20dull%20indeed%20if%20breezy%20tastes%20do%20not%20follow%20her%20through%20life%2C%20and%20forbid%20any%20of%20her%20days%20to%20be%20empty%20of%20intelligent%20enjoyment.%20%22Keep%20your%20years%20beautiful%3B%20make%20your%20own%20atmosphere%2C