cutive%20and%20Director%20gbnewby%40pglaf.org%20Section%204.%20Information%20about%20Donations%20to%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20depends%20upon%20and%20cannot%20survive%20without%20wide%20spread%20public%20support%20and%20donations%20to%20carry%20out%20its%20mission%20of%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20public%20domain%20and%20licensed%20works%20that%20can%20be%20freely%20distributed%20in%20machine%20readable%20form%20accessible%20by%20the%20widest%20array%20of%20equipment%20including%20outdated%20equipment.%20Many%20small%20donations%20(%241%20to%20%245%2C000)%20are%20particularly%20important%20to%20maintaining%20tax%20exempt%20status%20with%20the%20IRS.%20The%20Foundation%20is%20committed%20to%20complying%20with%20the%20laws%20regulating%20charities%20and%20charitable%20donations%20in%20all%2050%20states%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20Compliance%20requirements%20are%20not%20uniform%20and%20it%20takes%20a%20considerable%20effort%2C%20much%20paperwork%20and%20many%20fees%20to%20meet%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20these%20requirements.%20We%20do%20not%20solicit%20donations%20in%20locations%20where%20we%20have%20not%20received%20written%20confirmation%20of%20compliance.%20To%20SEND%20DONATIONS%20or%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20compliance%20for%20any%20particular%20state%20visit%20http%3A%2F%2Fpglaf.org%20While%20we%20cannot%20and%20do%20not%20solicit%20contributions%20from%20states%20where%20we%20have%20not%20met%20the%20solicitation%20requirements%2C%20we%20know%20of%20no%20prohibition%20against%20accepting%20unsolicited%20donations%20from%20donors%20in%20such%20states%20who%20approach%20us%20with%20offers%20to%20donate.%20International%20donations%20are%20gratefully%20accepted%2C%20but%20we%20cannot%20make%20any%20statements%20concerning%20tax%20treatment%20of%20donations%20received%20from%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%20U.S.%20laws%20alone%20swamp%20our%20small%20staff.%20Please%20check%20the%20Pr