0Gutenberg%20License%20included%20with%20this%20eBook%20or%20online%20at%20www.gutenberg.net%20Title%3A%20Why%20go%20to%20College%3F%20an%20Address%20Author%3A%20Alice%20Freeman%20Palmer%20Posting%20Date%3A%20November%205%2C%202008%20%5BEBook%20%232361%5D%20Release%20Date%3A%20October%2C%202000%20Language%3A%20English%20Character%20set%20encoding%3A%20ASCII%20***%20START%20OF%20THIS%20PROJECT%20GUTENBERG%20EBOOK%20WHY%20GO%20TO%20COLLEGE%3F%20AN%20ADDRESS%20***%20Produced%20by%20Stephanie%20L.%20Johnson.%20HTML%20version%20by%20Al%20Haines.%20WHY%20GO%20TO%20COLLEGE%3F%20an%20Address%20BY%20ALICE%20FREEMAN%20PALMER%20Formerly%20President%20of%20Wellesley%20College%20To%20a%20largely%20increasing%20number%20of%20young%20girls%20college%20doors%20are%20opening%20every%20year.%20Every%20year%20adds%20to%20the%20number%20of%20men%20who%20feel%20as%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20a%20successful%20lawyer%20in%20a%20great%20city%2C%20felt%20when%20in%20talking%20of%20the%20future%20of%20his%20four%20little%20children%20he%20said%2C%20%22For%20the%20two%20boys%20it%20is%20not%20so%20serious%2C%20but%20I%20lie%20down%20at%20night%20afraid%20to%20die%20and%20leave%20my%20daughters%20only%20a%20bank%20account.%22%20Year%20by%20year%2C%20too%2C%20the%20experiences%20of%20life%20are%20teaching%20mothers%20that%20happiness%20does%20not%20necessarily%20come%20to%20their%20daughters%20when%20accounts%20are%20large%20and%20banks%20are%20sound%2C%20but%20that%20on%20the%20contrary%20they%20take%20grave%20risks%20when%20they%20trust%20everything%20to%20accumulated%20wealth%20and%20the%20chance%20of%20a%20happy%20marriage.%20Our%20American%20girls%20themselves%20are%20becoming%20aware%20that%20they%20need%20the%20stimulus%2C%20the%20discipline%2C%20the%20knowledge%2C%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20college%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20school%2C%20if%20they%20are%20to%20prepare%20themselves%20for%20the%20most%20serviceable%20lives.%20But%20there%20are%20still%20parents%20who%20say%2C%20%22There%20is%20no%20need%20that%20my%20daughter%20should%20teach%3B%20then%20why%20should%20she%20go%20to%20college%3F%22%20I%20will%20not%20reply%20that%20college%20training%20is%20a%20life%20insurance%20for%20a%20girl%2C%20a%20pledge%20that%20she%20possesses%20the%20disciplined%20ability%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20for%20herself%20and%20others%20in%20case%20of%20need%2C%20for%20I%20prefer%20to%20insist%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20giving%20every%20girl%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20her%20present%20circumstances%2C%20a%20special%20training%20in%20some%20one%20thing%20by%20which%20she%20can%20render%20society%20service%2C%20not%20amateur%20but%20of%20an%20expert%20sort%2C%20and%20service%20too%20for%20which%20it%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20price.%20The%20number%20of%20families%20will%20surely%20increase%20who%20will%20follow%20the%20example%20of%20an%20eminent%20banker%20whose%20daughters%20have%20been%20given%20each%20her%20specialty.%20One%20has%20chosen%20music%2C%20and%20has%20gone%20far%20with%20the%20best%20masters%20in%20this%20country%20and%20in%20Europe%2C%20so%20far%20that%20she%20now%20holds%20a%20high%20rank%20among%20musicians%20at%20home%20and%20abroad.%20Another%20has%20taken%20art%2C%20and%20has%20not%20been%20content%20to%20paint%20pretty%20gifts%20for%20her%20friends%2C%20but%20in%20the%20studios%20of%20New%20York%2C%20Munich%2C%20and%20Paris%2C%20she%20has%20won%20the%20right%20to%20be%20called%20an%20artist%2C%20and%20in%20her%20studio%20at%20home%20to%20paint%20portraits%20which%20have%20a%20market%20value.%20A%20third%20has%20proved%20that%20she%20can%20earn%20her%20living%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20by%20her%20exquisite%20jellies%2C%20preserves%2C%20and%20sweetmeats.%20Yet%20the%20house%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20the%20house%20by%20the%20sea%2C%20and%20the%20friends%20in%20the%20city%20are%20not%20neglected%2C%20nor%20are%20these%20young%20women%20found%20less%20attractive%20because%20of%20their%20special%20accomplishments.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20true%20that%20all%20girls%20should%20go%20to%20college%20any%20more%20than%20that%20all%20boys%20should%20go%2C%20it%20is%20nevertheless%20true%20that%20they%20should%20go%20in%20greater%20numbers%20than%20at%20present.%20They%20fail%20to%20go%20because%20they%2C%20their%20parents%20and%20their%20teachers%2C%20do%20not%20see%20clearly%20the%20personal%20benefits%20distinct%20from%20the%20commercial%20value%20of%20a%20college%20training.%20I%20wish%20here%20to%20discuss%20these%20benefits%2C%20these%20larger%20gifts%20of%20the%20college%20life%2C--what%20they%20may%20be%2C%20and%20for%20whom%20they%20are%20waiting.%20It%20is%20undoubtedly%20true%20that%20many%20girls%20are%20totally%20unfitted%20by%20home%20and%20school%20life%20for%20a%20valuable%20college%20course.%20These%20joys%20and%20successes%2C%20these%20high%20interests%20and%20friendships%2C%20are%20not%20for%20the%20self-conscious%20and%20nervous%20invalid%2C%20nor%20for%20her%20who%20in%20the%20exuberance%20of%20youth%20recklessly%20ignores%20the%20laws%20of%20a%20healthy%20life.%20The%20good%20society%20of%20scholars%20and%20of%20libraries%20and%20laboratories%20has%20no%20place%20and%20no%20attraction%20for%20her%20who%20finds%20no%20message%20in%20Plato%2C%20no%20beauty%20in%20mathematical%20order%2C%20and%20who%20never%20longs%20to%20know%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20stars%20over%20her%20head%20or%20the%20flowers%20under%20her%20feet.%20Neither%20will%20the%20finer%20opportunities%20of%20college%20life%20appeal%20to%20one%20who%2C%20until%20she%20is%20eighteen%20(is%20there%20such%20a%20girl%20in%20this%20country%3F)%2C%20has%20felt%20no%20passion%20for%20the%20service%20of%20others%2C%20no%20desire%20to%20know%20if%20through%20history%20or%20philosophy%2C%20or%20any%20study%20of%20the%20laws%20of%20society%2C%20she%20can%20learn%20why%20the%20world%20is%20so%20sad%2C%20so%20hard%2C%20so%20selfish%20as%20she%20finds%20it%2C%20even%20when%20she%20looks%20upon%20it%20from%20the%20most%20sheltered%20life.%20No%2C%20the%20college%20cannot%20be%2C%20should%20not%20try%20to%20be%2C%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20hospital%2C%20reformatory%20or%20kindergarten.%20To%20do%20its%20best%20work%20it%20should%20be%20organized%20for%20the%20strong%2C%20not%20for%20the%20weak%3B%20for%20the%20high-minded%2C%20self-controlled%2C%20generous%2C%20and%20courageous%20spirits%2C%20not%20for%20the%20indifferent%2C%20the%20dull%2C%20the%20idle%2C%20or%20those%20who%20are%20already%20forming%20their%20characters%20on%20the%20amusement%20theory%20of%20life.%20All%20these%20perverted%20young%20people%20may%2C%20and%20often%20do%2C%20get%20large%20benefit%20and%20invigoration%2C%20new%20ideals%2C%20and%20unselfish%20purposes%20from%20their%20four%20years%26%2339%3B%20companionship%20with%20teachers%20and%20comrades%20of%20a%20higher%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20and%20moral%20stature%20than%20their%20own.%20I%20have%20seen%20girls%20change%20so%20much%20in%20college%20that%20I%20have%20wondered%20if%20their%20friends%20at%20home%20would%20know%20them%2C--the%20voice%2C%20the%20carriage%2C%20the%20unconscious%20manner%2C%20all%20telling%20a%20story%20of%20new%20tastes%20and%20habits%20and%20loves%20and%20interests%2C%20that%20had%20wrought%20out%20in%20very%20truth%20a%20new%20creature.%20Yet%20in%20spite%20of%20this%20I%20have%20sometimes%20thought%20that%20in%20college%20more%20than%20elsewhere%20the%20old%20law%20holds%2C%20%22To%20him%20that%20hath%20shall%20be%20given%20and%20he%20shall%20have%20abundance%2C%20but%20from%20him%20who%20hath%20not%20shall%20be%20taken%20away%20even%20that%20which%20he%20seemeth%20to%20have.%22%20For%20it%20is%20the%20young%20life%20which%20is%20open%20and%20prepared%20to%20receive%20which%20obtains%20the%20gracious%20and%20uplifting%20influences%20of%20college%20days.%20What%2C%20then%2C%20for%20such%20persons%20are%20the%20rich%20and%20abiding%20rewards%20of%20study%20in%20college%20or%20university%3F%20Pre-eminently%20the%20college%20is%20a%20place%20of%20education.%20That%20is%20the%20ground%20of%20its%20being.%20We%20go%20to%20college%20to%20know%2C%20assured%20that%20knowledge%20is%20sweet%20and%20powerful%2C%20that%20a%20good%20education%20emancipates%20the%20mind%20and%20makes%20us%20citizens%20of%20the%20world.%20No%20college%20which%20does%20not%20thoroughly%20educate%20can%20be%20called%20good%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20else%20it%20does.%20No%20student%20who%20fails%20to%20get%20a%20little%20knowledge%20on%20many%20subjects%2C%20and%20much%20knowledge%20on%20some%2C%20can%20be%20said%20to%20have%20succeeded%2C%20whatever%20other%20advantages%20she%20may%20have%20found%20by%20the%20way.%20It%20is%20a%20beautiful%20and%20significant%20fact%20that%20in%20all%20times%20the%20years%20of%20learning%20have%20been%20also%20the%20years%20of%20romance.%20Those%20who%20love%20girls%20and%20boys%20pray%20that%20our%20colleges%20may%20be%20homes%20of%20sound%20learning%2C%20for%20knowledge%20is%20the%20condition%20of%20every%20college%20blessing.%20%22Let%20no%20man%20incapable%20of%20mathematics%20enter%20here%2C%22%20Plato%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20inscribed%20over%20his%20Academy%20door.%20%22Let%20no%20one%20to%20whom%20hard%20study%20is%20repulsive%20hope%20for%20anything%20from%20us%2C%22%20American%20colleges%20might%20paraphrase.%20Accordingly%20in%20my%20talk%20today%20I%20shall%20say%20little%20of%20the%20direct%20benefits%20of%20knowledge%20which%20the%20college%20affords.%20These%20may%20be%20assumed.%20It%20is%20on%20their%20account%20that%20one%20knocks%20at%20the%20college%20door.%20But%20seeking%20this%20first%2C%20a%20good%20many%20other%20things%20are%20added.%20I%20want%20to%20point%20out%20some%20of%20these%20collateral%20advantages%20of%20going%20to%20college%2C%20or%20rather%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20some%20of%20the%20many%20forms%20in%20which%20the%20winning%20of%20knowledge%20presents%20itself.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20happiness.%20Everybody%20wants%20%22a%20good%20time%2C%22%20especially%20every%20girl%20in%20her%20teens.%20A%20good%20time%2C%20it%20is%20true%2C%20does%20not%20always%20in%20these%20years%20mean%20what%20it%20will%20mean%20by%20and%20by%2C%20any%20more%20than%20the%20girl%20of%20eighteen%20plays%20with%20the%20doll%20which%20entranced%20the%20child%20of%20eight.%20It%20takes%20some%20time%20to%20discover%20that%20work%20is%20the%20best%20sort%20of%20play%2C%20and%20some%20people%20never%20discover%20it%20at%20all.%20But%20when%20mothers%20ask%20such%20questions%20as%20these%3A%20%22How%20can%20I%20make%20my%20daughter%20happy%3F%22%20%22How%20can%20I%20give%20her%20the%20best%20society%3F%22%20%22How%20can%20she%20have%20a%20good%20time%3F%22%20the%20answer%20in%20most%20cases%20is%20simple.%20Send%20her%20to%20college%2C--to%20almost%20any%20college.%20Send%20her%20because%20there%20is%20no%20other%20place%20where%20between%20eighteen%20and%20twenty-two%20she%20is%20so%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20genuinely%20good%20time.%20Merely%20for%20good%20times%2C%20for%20romance%2C%20for%20society%2C%20college%20life%20offers%20unequalled%20opportunities.%20Of%20course%20no%20idle%20person%20can%20possibly%20be%20happy%2C%20even%20for%20a%20day%2C%20nor%20she%20who%20makes%20a%20business%20of%20trying%20to%20amuse%20herself.%20For%20full%20happiness%2C%20though%20its%20springs%20are%20within%2C%20we%20want%20health%20and%20friends%20and%20work%20and%20objects%20of%20aspiration.%20%22We%20live%20by%20admiration%2C%20hope%2C%20and%20love%2C%22%20says%20Wordsworth.%20The%20college%20abounds%20in%20all%20three.%20In%20the%20college%20time%20new%20powers%20are%20sprouting%2C%20and%20intelligence%2C%20merriment%2C%20truthfulness%20and%20generosity%20are%20more%20natural%20than%20the%20opposite%20qualities%20often%20become%20in%20later%20years.%20An%20exhilarating%20atmosphere%20pervades%20the%20place.%20We%20who%20are%20in%20it%20all%20the%20time%20feel%20that%20we%20live%20at%20the%20fountain%20of%20perpetual%20youth%2C%20and%20those%20who%20take%20but%20a%20four%20years%26%2339%3B%20bath%20in%20it%20become%20more%20cheerful%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20full%20of%20promise%20than%20they%20are%20ever%20likely%20to%20find%20themselves%20again%3B%20for%20a%20college%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20compendium%20of%20the%20things%20that%20most%20men%20long%20for.%20It%20is%20usually%20planted%20in%20a%20beautiful%20spot%2C%20the%20charm%20of%20trees%20and%20water%20being%20added%20to%20stately%20buildings%20and%20stimulating%20works%20of%20art.%20Venerable%20associations%20of%20the%20past%20hallow%20its%20halls.%20Leaders%20in%20the%20stirring%20world%20of%20to-day%20return%20at%20each%20commencement%20to%20share%20the%20fresh%20life%20of%20the%20new%20class.%20Books%2C%20pictures%2C%20music%2C%20collections%2C%20appliances%20in%20every%20field%2C%20learned%20teachers%2C%20mirthful%20friends%2C%20athletics%20for%20holidays%2C%20the%20best%20words%20of%20the%20best%20men%20for%20holy%20days%2C--all%20are%20here.%20No%20wonder%20that%20men%20look%20back%20upon%20their%20college%20life%20as%20upon%20halcyon%20days%2C%20the%20romantic%20period%20of%20youth.%20No%20wonder%20that%20Dr.%20Holmes%26%2339%3Bs%20poems%20to%20his%20Harvard%20classmates%20find%20an%20echo%20in%20college%20reunions%20everywhere%3B%20and%20gray-haired%20men%2C%20who%20outside%20the%20narrowing%20circle%20of%20home%20have%20not%20heard%20their%20first%20names%20for%20years%2C%20remain%20Bill%20and%20Joe%20and%20John%20and%20George%20to%20college%20comrades%2C%20even%20if%20unseen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20generation.%20Yet%20a%20girl%20should%20go%20to%20college%20not%20merely%20to%20obtain%20four%20happy%20years%20but%20to%20make%20a%20second%20gain%2C%20which%20is%20often%20overlooked%2C%20and%20is%20little%20understood%20even%20when%20perceived%3B%20I%20mean%20a%20gain%20in%20health.%20The%20old%20notion%20that%20low%20vitality%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20course%20with%20women%3B%20that%20to%20be%20delicate%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20superior%20refinement%2C%20especially%20in%20well-to-do%20families%3B%20that%20sickness%20is%20a%20dispensation%20of%20Providence%2C--these%20notions%20meet%20with%20no%20acceptance%20in%20college.%20Years%20ago%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20mirror%20frame%20of%20a%20college%20freshman%26%2339%3Bs%20room%20this%20little%20formula%3A%20%22Sickness%20is%20carelessness%2C%20carelessness%20is%20selfishness%2C%20and%20selfishness%20is%20sin.%22%20And%20I%20have%20often%20noticed%20among%20college%20girls%20an%20air%20of%20humiliation%20and%20shame%20when%20obliged%20to%20confess%20a%20lack%20of%20physical%20vigor%2C%20as%20if%20they%20were%20convicted%20of%20managing%20life%20with%20bad%20judgment%2C%20or%20of%20some%20moral%20delinquency.%20With%20the%20spreading%20scientific%20conviction%20that%20health%20is%20a%20matter%20largely%20under%20each%20person%26%2339%3Bs%20control%2C%20that%20even%20inherited%20tendencies%20to%20disease%20need%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20run%20their%20riotous%20course%20unchecked%2C%20there%20comes%20an%20earnest%20purpose%20to%20be%20strong%20and%20free.%20Fascinating%20fields%20of%20knowledge%20are%20waiting%20to%20be%20explored%3B%20possibilities%20of%20doing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20knowing%2C%20are%20on%20every%20side%3B%20new%20and%20dear%20friendships%20enlarge%20and%20sweeten%20dreams%20of%20future%20study%20and%20work%2C%20and%20the%20young%20student%20cannot%20afford%20quivering%20nerves%20or%20small%20lungs%20or%20an%20aching%20head%20any%20more%20than%20bad%20taste%2C%20rough%20manners%2C%20or%20a%20weak%20will.%20Handicapped%20by%20inheritance%20or%20bad%20training%2C%20she%20finds%20the%20plan%20of%20college%20life%20itself%20her%20supporter%20and%20friend.%20The%20steady%2C%20long-continued%20routine%20of%20mental%20work%2C%20physical%20exercise%2C%20recreation%2C%20and%20sleep%2C%20the%20simple%20and%20wholesome%20food%2C%20in%20place%20of%20irregular%20and%20unstudied%20diet%2C%20work%20out%20salvation%20for%20her.%20Instead%20of%20being%20left%20to%20go%20out-of-doors%20when%20she%20feels%20like%20it%2C%20the%20regular%20training%20of%20the%20gymnasium%2C%20the%20boats%20on%20lake%20and%20river%2C%20the%20tennis%20court%2C%20the%20golf%20links%2C%20the%20basket%20ball%2C%20the%20bicycle%2C%20the%20long%20walk%20among%20the%20woods%20in%20search%20of%20botanical%20or%20geological%20specimens%2C--all%20these%20and%20many%20more%20call%20to%20the%20busy%20student%2C%20until%20she%20realizes%20that%20they%20have%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20every%20well-ordered%20day%20of%20every%20month.%20So%20she%20learns%2C%20little%20by%20little%2C%20that%20buoyant%20health%20is%20a%20precious%20possession%20to%20be%20won%20and%20kept.%20It%20is%20significant%20that%20already%20statistical%20investigation%20in%20this%20country%20and%20in%20England%20shows%20that%20the%20standard%20of%20health%20is%20higher%20among%20the%20women%20who%20hold%20college%20degrees%20than%20among%20any%20other%20equal%20number%20of%20the%20same%20age%20and%20class.%20And%20it%20is%20interesting%20also%20to%20observe%20to%20what%20sort%20of%20questions%20our%20recent%20girl%20graduates%20have%20been%20inclined%20to%20devote%20attention.%20They%20have%20been%20largely%20the%20neglected%20problems%20of%20little%20children%20and%20their%20health%2C%20of%20home%20sanitation%2C%20of%20food%20and%20its%20choice%20and%20preparation%2C%20of%20domestic%20service%2C%20of%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20schools%20and%20public%20buildings.%20Colleges%20for%20girls%20are%20pledged%20by%20their%20very%20constitution%20to%20make%20persistent%20war%20on%20the%20water%20cure%2C%20the%20nervine%20retreat%2C%20the%20insane%20asylum%2C%20the%20hospital%2C--those%20bitter%20fruits%20of%20the%20emotional%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20women.%20%22I%20can%20never%20afford%20a%20sick%20headache%20again%2C%20life%20is%20so%20interesting%20and%20there%20is%20so%20much%20to%20do%2C%22%20a%20delicate%20girl%20said%20to%20me%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20college%20year.%20And%20while%20her%20mother%20was%20in%20a%20far-off%20invalid%20retreat%2C%20she%20undertook%20the%20battle%20against%20fate%20with%20the%20same%20intelligence%20and%20courage%20which%20she%20put%20into%20her%20calculus%20problems%20and%20her%20translations%20of%20Sophocles.%20Her%20beautiful%20home%20and%20her%20rosy%20and%20happy%20children%20prove%20the%20measure%20of%20her%20hard-won%20success.%20Formerly%20the%20majority%20of%20physicians%20had%20but%20one%20question%20for%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20nervous%20and%20delicate%20girl%2C%20%22Does%20she%20go%20to%20school%3F%22%20And%20only%20one%20prescription%2C%20%22Take%20her%20out%20of%20school.%22%20Never%20a%20suggestion%20as%20to%20suppers%20of%20pickles%20and%20pound-cake%2C%20never%20a%20hint%20about%20midnight%20dancing%20and%20hurried%20day-time%20ways.%20But%20now%20the%20sensible%20doctor%20asks%2C%20%22What%20are%20her%20interests%3F%20What%20are%20her%20tastes%3F%20What%20are%20her%20habits%3F%22%20And%20he%20finds%20new%20interests%20for%20her%2C%20and%20urges%20the%20formation%20of%20out-of-door%20tastes%20and%20steady%20occupation%20for%20the%20mind%2C%20in%20order%20to%20draw%20the%20morbid%20girl%20from%20herself%20into%20the%20invigorating%20world%20outside.%20This%20the%20college%20does%20largely%20through%20its%20third%20gift%20of%20friendship.%20Until%20a%20girl%20goes%20away%20from%20home%20to%20school%20or%20college%2C%20her%20friends%20are%20chiefly%20chosen%20for%20her%20by%20circumstances.%20Her%20young%20relatives%2C%20her%20neighbors%20in%20the%20same%20street%2C%20those%20who%20happen%20to%20go%20to%20the%20same%20school%20or%20church%2C--these%20she%20makes%20her%20girlish%20intimates.%20She%20goes%20to%20college%20with%20the%20entire%20conviction%2C%20half%20unknown%20to%20herself%2C%20that%20her%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20political%20party%20contains%20all%20the%20honest%20men%2C%20her%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20circle%20all%20the%20true%20ladies%2C%20her%20church%20all%20the%20real%20saints%20of%20the%20community.%20And%20the%20smaller%20the%20town%2C%20the%20more%20absolute%20is%20her%20belief.%20But%20in%20college%20she%20finds%20that%20the%20girl%20who%20earned%20her%20scholarship%20in%20the%20village%20school%20sits%20beside%20the%20banker%26%2339%3Bs%20daughter%3B%20the%20New%20England%20farmer%26%2339%3Bs%20child%20rooms%20next%20the%20heiress%20of%20a%20Hawaiian%20sugar%20plantation%3B%20the%20daughters%20of%20the%20opposing%20candidates%20in%20a%20sharply%20fought%20election%20have%20grown%20great%20friends%20in%20college%20boats%20and%20laboratories%3B%20and%20before%20her%20diploma%20is%20won%20she%20realizes%20how%20much%20richer%20a%20world%20she%20lives%20in%20than%20she%20ever%20dreamed%20of%20at%20home.%20The%20wealth%20that%20lies%20in%20differences%20has%20dawned%20upon%20her%20vision.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%20sit%20down%20together%20that%20either%20can%20understand%20how%20the%20Lord%20is%20the%20Maker%20of%20them%20all.%20To-day%20above%20all%20things%20we%20need%20the%20influence%20of%20men%20and%20women%20of%20friendliness%2C%20of%20generous%20nature%2C%20of%20hospitality%20to%20new%20ideas%2C%20in%20short%2C%20of%20social%20imagination.%20But%20instead%2C%20we%20find%20each%20political%20party%20bitterly%20calling%20the%20other%20dishonest%2C%20each%20class%20suspicious%20of%20the%20intentions%20of%20the%20other%2C%20and%20in%20social%20life%20the%20pettiest%20standards%20of%20conduct.%20Is%20it%20not%20well%20for%20us%20that%20the%20colleges%20all%20over%20the%20country%20still%20offer%20to%20their%20fortunate%20students%20a%20society%20of%20the%20most%20democratic%20sort%2C--one%20in%20which%20a%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20money%2C%20a%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20position%2C%20can%20assure%20no%20distinction%20and%20make%20no%20close%20friends%3F%20Here%20capacity%20of%20every%20kind%20counts%20for%20its%20full%20value.%20Here%20enthusiasm%20waits%20to%20make%20heroes%20of%20those%20who%20can%20lead.%20Here%20charming%20manners%2C%20noble%20character%2C%20amiable%20temper%2C%20scholarly%20power%2C%20find%20their%20full%20opportunity%20and%20inspire%20such%20friendships%20as%20are%20seldom%20made%20afterward.%20I%20have%20forgotten%20my%20chemistry%2C%20and%20my%20classical%20philology%20cannot%20bear%20examination%3B%20but%20all%20round%20the%20world%20there%20are%20men%20and%20women%20at%20work%2C%20my%20intimates%20of%20college%20days%2C%20who%20have%20made%20the%20wide%20earth%20a%20friendly%20place%20to%20me.%20Of%20every%20creed%2C%20of%20every%20party%2C%20in%20far-away%20places%20and%20in%20near%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20them%20makes%20me%20more%20courageous%20in%20duty%20and%20more%20faithful%20to%20opportunity%2C%20though%20for%20many%20years%20we%20may%20not%20have%20had%20time%20to%20write%20each%20other%20a%20letter.%20The%20basis%20of%20all%20valuable%20and%20enduring%20friendships%20is%20not%20accident%20or%20juxtaposition%2C%20but%20tastes%2C%20interests%2C%20habits%2C%20work%2C%20ambitions.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20to%20college%20friendship%20clings%20a%20romance%20entirely%20its%20own.%20One%20of%20the%20friends%20may%20spend%20her%20days%20in%20the%20laboratory%2C%20eagerly%20chasing%20the%20shy%20facts%20that%20hide%20beyond%20the%20microscope%26%2339%3Bs%20fine%20vision%2C%20and%20the%20other%20may%20fill%20her%20hours%20and%20her%20heart%20with%20the%20poets%20and%20the%20philosophers%3B%20one%20may%20steadfastly%20pursue%20her%20way%20toward%20the%20command%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20other%20towards%20the%20world%20of%20letters%20and%20of%20art%3B%20these%20divergences%20constitute%20no%20barrier%2C%20but%20rather%20an%20aid%20to%20the%20fulness%20of%20friendship.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20goes%20in%20a%20simple%20gown%20which%20she%20has%20earned%20and%20made%20herself%2C%20and%20the%20other%20lives%20when%20at%20home%20in%20a%20merchant%26%2339%3Bs%20modern%20palace--what%20has%20that%20to%20do%20with%20the%20things%20the%20girls%20care%20about%20and%20the%20dreams%20they%20talk%20over%20in%20the%20walk%20by%20the%20river%20or%20the%20bicycle%20ride%20through%20country%20roads%3F%20If%20any%20young%20man%20to-day%20goes%20through%20Harvard%20lonely%2C%20neglected%2C%20unfriended%2C%20if%20any%20girl%20lives%20solitary%20and%20wretched%20in%20her%20life%20at%20Wellesley%2C%20it%20is%20their%20own%20fault.%20It%20must%20be%20because%20they%20are%20suspicious%2C%20unfriendly%20or%20disagreeable%20themselves.%20Certainly%20it%20is%20true%20that%20in%20the%20associations%20of%20college%20life%2C%20more%20than%20in%20any%20other%20that%20the%20country%20can%20show%2C%20what%20is%20extraneous%2C%20artificial%2C%20and%20temporary%20falls%20away%2C%20and%20the%20every-day%20relations%20of%20life%20and%20work%20take%20on%20a%20character%20that%20is%20simple%2C%20natural%2C%20genuine.%20And%20so%20it%20comes%20about%20that%20the%20fourth%20gift%20of%20college%20life%20is%20ideals%20of%20personal%20character.%20To%20some%20people%20the%20shaping%20ideals%20of%20what%20character%20should%20be%2C%20often%20held%20unconsciously%2C%20come%20from%20the%20books%20they%20are%20given%20by%20the%20persons%20whom%20they%20most%20admire%20before%20they%20are%20twenty%20years%20old.%20The%20greatest%20thing%20any%20friend%20or%20teacher%2C%20either%20in%20school%20or%20college%2C%20can%20do%20for%20a%20student%20is%20to%20furnish%20him%20with%20a%20personal%20ideal.%20The%20college%20professors%20who%20transformed%20me%20through%20my%20acquaintance%20with%20them--ah%2C%20they%20were%20few%2C%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20dozen%20conversations%20with%20them%20outside%20their%20class%20rooms--gave%20me%2C%20each%20in%20his%20different%20way%2C%20an%20ideal%20of%20character%2C%20of%20conduct%2C%20of%20the%20scholar%2C%20the%20leader%2C%20of%20which%20they%20and%20I%20were%20totally%20unconscious%20at%20the%20time.%20For%20many%20years%20I%20have%20known%20that%20my%20study%20with%20them%2C%20no%20matter%20whether%20of%20philosophy%20or%20of%20Greek%2C%20of%20mathematics%20or%20history%20or%20English%2C%20enlarged%20my%20notions%20of%20life%2C%20uplifted%20my%20standards%20of%20culture%2C%20and%20so%20inspired%20me%20with%20new%20possibilities%20of%20usefulness%20and%20of%20happiness.%20Not%20the%20facts%20and%20theories%20that%20I%20learned%20so%20much%20as%20the%20men%20who%20taught%20me%2C%20gave%20this%20inspiration.%20The%20community%20at%20large%20is%20right%20in%20saying%20that%20it%20wants%20the%20personal%20influence%20of%20professors%20on%20students%2C%20but%20it%20is%20wholly%20wrong%20in%20assuming%20that%20this%20precious%20influence%20comes%20from%20frequent%20meetings%20or%20talks%20on%20miscellaneous%20subjects.%20There%20is%20quite%20as%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20quickening%20force%20in%20the%20somewhat%20remote%20and%20mysterious%20power%20of%20the%20teacher%20who%20devotes%20himself%20to%20amassing%20treasures%20of%20scholarship%2C%20or%20to%20patiently%20working%20out%20the%20best%20methods%20of%20teaching%3B%20who%20standing%20somewhat%20apart%2C%20still%20remains%20an%20ideal%20of%20the%20Christian%20scholar%2C%20the%20just%2C%20the%20courteous%20man%20or%20woman.%20To%20come%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20one%20such%20teacher%20is%20enough%20to%20make%20college%20life%20worthwhile.%20A%20young%20man%20who%20came%20to%20Harvard%20with%20eighty%20cents%20in%20his%20pocket%2C%20and%20worked%20his%20way%20through%2C%20never%20a%20high%20scholar%2C%20and%20now%20in%20a%20business%20which%20looks%20very%20commonplace%2C%20told%20me%20the%20other%20day%20that%20he%20would%20not%20care%20to%20be%20alive%20if%20he%20had%20not%20gone%20to%20college.%20His%20face%20flushed%20as%20he%20explained%20how%20different%20his%20days%20would%20have%20been%20if%20he%20had%20not%20known%20two%20of%20his%20professors.%20%22Do%20you%20use%20your%20college%20studies%20in%20your%20business%3F%22%20I%20asked.%20%22Oh%2C%20no!%22%20he%20answered.%20%22But%20I%20am%20another%20man%20in%20doing%20the%20business%3B%20and%20when%20the%20day%26%2339%3Bs%20work%20is%20done%20I%20live%20another%20life%20because%20of%20my%20college%20experiences.%20The%20business%20and%20I%20are%20both%20the%20better%20for%20it%20every%20day.%22%20How%20many%20a%20young%20girl%20has%20had%20her%20whole%20horizon%20extended%20by%20the%20changed%20ideals%20she%20gained%20in%20college!%20Yet%20this%20is%20largely%20because%20the%20associations%20and%20studies%20there%20are%20likely%20to%20give%20her%20permanent%20interests--the%20fifth%20and%20perhaps%20the%20greatest%20gift%20of%20college%20life%20of%20which%20I%20shall%20speak.%20The%20old%20fairy%20story%20which%20charmed%20us%20in%20childhood%20ended%20with--%22And%20they%20were%20married%20and%20lived%20happy%20ever%20after.%22%20It%20conducted%20to%20the%20altar%2C%20having%20brought%20the%20happy%20pair%20through%20innumerable%20difficulties%2C%20and%20left%20us%20with%20the%20contented%20sense%20that%20all%20the%20mistakes%20and%20problems%20would%20now%20vanish%20and%20life%20be%20one%20long%20day%20of%20unclouded%20bliss.%20I%20have%20seen%20devoted%20and%20intelligent%20mothers%20arrange%20their%20young%20daughters%26%2339%3B%20education%20and%20companionships%20precisely%20on%20this%20basis.%20They%20planned%20as%20if%20these%20pretty%20and%20charming%20girls%20were%20going%20to%20live%20only%20twenty%20or%20twenty-five%20years%20at%20the%20utmost%2C%20and%20had%20consequently%20no%20need%20of%20the%20wealthy%20interests%20that%20should%20round%20out%20the%20full-grown%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20stature%2C%20making%20her%20younger%20in%20feeling%20at%20forty%20than%20at%20twenty%2C%20and%20more%20lovely%20and%20admired%20at%20eighty%20than%20at%20either.%20Emerson%20in%20writing%20of%20beauty%20declares%20that%20%22the%20secret%20of%20ugliness%20consists%20not%20in%20irregular%20outline%2C%20but%20in%20being%20uninteresting.%20We%20love%20any%20forms%2C%20however%20ugly%2C%20from%20which%20great%20qualities%20shine.%20If%20command%2C%20eloquence%2C%20art%2C%20or%20invention%20exists%20in%20the%20most%20deformed%20person%2C%20all%20the%20accidents%20that%20usually%20displease%2C%20please%2C%20and%20raise%20esteem%20and%20wonder%20higher.%20Beauty%20without%20grace%20is%20the%20head%20without%20the%20body.%20Beauty%20without%20expression%20tires.%22%20Of%20course%20such%20considerations%20can%20hardly%20come%20with%20full%20force%20to%20the%20young%20girl%20herself%2C%20who%20feels%20aged%20at%20eighteen%2C%20and%20imagines%20that%20the%20troubles%20and%20problems%20of%20life%20and%20thought%20are%20hers%20already.%20%22Oh%2C%20tell%20me%20to-night%2C%22%20cried%20a%20college%20freshman%20once%20to%20her%20President%2C%20%22which%20is%20the%20right%20side%20and%20which%20is%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20this%20Andover%20question%20about%20eschatology%3F%22%20The%20young%20girl%20is%20impatient%20of%20open%20questions%2C%20and%20irritated%20at%20her%20inability%20to%20answer%20them.%20Neither%20can%20she%20believe%20that%20the%20first%20headlong%20zest%20with%20which%20she%20throws%20herself%20into%20society%2C%20athletics%2C%20into%20everything%20which%20comes%20in%20her%20way%2C%20can%20ever%20fail.%20But%20her%20elders%20know%2C%20looking%20on%2C%20that%20our%20American%20girl%2C%20the%20comrade%20of%20her%20parents%20and%20of%20her%20brothers%20and%20their%20friends%2C%20brought%20up%20from%20babyhood%20in%20the%20eager%20talk%20of%20politics%20and%20society%2C%20of%20religious%20belief%2C%20of%20public%20action%2C%20of%20social%20responsibility--that%20this%20typical%20girl%2C%20with%20her%20quick%20sympathies%2C%20her%20clear%20head%2C%20her%20warm%20heart%2C%20her%20outreaching%20hands%2C%20will%20not%20permanently%20be%20satisfied%20or%20self-respecting%2C%20though%20she%20have%20the%20prettiest%20dresses%20and%20hats%20in%20town%2C%20or%20the%20most%20charming%20of%20dinners%2C%20dances%2C%20and%20teas.%20Unless%20there%20comes%20to%20her%2C%20and%20comes%20early%2C%20the%20one%20chief%20happiness%20of%20life%2C--a%20marriage%20of%20comradeship%2C--she%20must%20face%20for%20herself%20the%20question%2C%20%22What%20shall%20I%20do%20with%20my%20life%3F%22%20I%20recall%20a%20superb%20girl%20of%20twenty%20as%20I%20overtook%20her%20one%20winter%20morning%20hurrying%20along%20Commonwealth%20Avenue.%20She%20spoke%20of%20a%20brilliant%20party%20at%20a%20friend%26%2339%3Bs%20the%20previous%20evening.%20%22But%2C%20oh!%22%20she%20cried%2C%20throwing%20up%20her%20hands%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20hopeless%20impatience%2C%20%22tell%20me%20what%20to%20do.%20My%20dancing%20days%20are%20over!%22%20I%20laughed%20at%20her%2C%20%22Have%20you%20sprained%20your%20ankle%3F%22%20But%20I%20saw%20I%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20when%20she%20added%2C%20%22It%20is%20no%20laughing%20matter.%20I%20have%20been%20out%20three%20years.%20I%20have%20not%20done%20what%20they%20expected%20of%20me%2C%22%20with%20a%20flush%20and%20a%20shrug%2C%20%22and%20there%20is%20a%20crowd%20of%20nice%20girls%20coming%20on%20this%20winter%3B%20and%20anyway%2C%20I%20am%20so%20tired%20of%20going%20to%20teas%20and%20ball-games%20and%20assemblies!%20I%20don%26%2339%3Bt%20care%20the%20least%20in%20the%20world%20for%20foreign%20missions%2C%20and%2C%22%20with%20a%20stamp%2C%20%22I%20am%20not%20going%20slumming%20among%20the%20Italians.%20I%20have%20too%20much%20respect%20for%20the%20Italians.%20And%20what%20shall%20I%20do%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%3F%22%20That%20was%20a%20frank%20statement%20of%20what%20any%20girl%20of%20brains%20or%20conscience%20feels%2C%20with%20more%20or%20less%20bitter%20distinctness%2C%20unless%20she%20marries%20early%2C%20or%20has%20some%20pressing%20work%20for%20which%20she%20is%20well%20trained.%20Yet%20even%20if%20that%20which%20is%20the%20profession%20of%20woman%20par%20excellence%20be%20hers%2C%20how%20can%20she%20be%20perennially%20so%20interesting%20a%20companion%20to%20her%20husband%20and%20children%20as%20if%20she%20had%20keen%20personal%20tastes%2C%20long%20her%20own%2C%20and%20growing%20with%20her%20growth%3F%20Indeed%2C%20in%20that%20respect%20the%20condition%20of%20men%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20women.%20It%20would%20be%20quite%20the%20same%20were%20it%20not%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20man%26%2339%3Bs%20business%20or%20profession%20is%20generally%20in%20itself%20a%20means%20of%20growth%2C%20of%20education%2C%20of%20dignity.%20He%20leans%20his%20life%20against%20it.%20He%20builds%20his%20home%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20it.%20It%20binds%20his%20days%20together%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20natural%20piety%20and%20makes%20him%20advance%20in%20strength%20and%20nobility%20as%20he%20%22fulfils%20the%20common%20round%2C%20the%20daily%20task.%22%20And%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20men%20in%20the%20past%2C%20if%20they%20have%20been%20honorable%20men%2C%20have%20grown%20old%20better%20than%20women.%20Men%20usually%20retain%20their%20ability%20longer%2C%20their%20mental%20alertness%20and%20hospitality.%20They%20add%20fine%20quality%20to%20fine%20quality%2C%20passing%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20preserving%20in%20old%20age%20whatever%20has%20been%20best%20in%20youth.%20It%20was%20a%20sudden%20recognition%20of%20this%20fact%20which%20made%20a%20young%20friend%20of%20mine%20say%20last%20winter%2C%20%22I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20parties%20any%20more%3B%20the%20men%20best%20worth%20talking%20with%20are%20too%20old%20to%20dance.%22%20Even%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20permanent%20business%20or%20profession%2C%20however%2C%20the%20most%20interesting%20men%20I%20know%20are%20those%20who%20have%20an%20avocation%20as%20well%20as%20a%20vocation.%20I%20mean%20a%20taste%20or%20work%20quite%20apart%20from%20the%20business%20of%20life.%20This%20revives%2C%20inspires%2C%20and%20cultivates%20them%20perpetually.%20It%20matters%20little%20what%20it%20is%2C%20if%20only%20it%20is%20real%20and%20personal%2C%20is%20large%20enough%20to%20last%2C%20and%20possesses%20the%20power%20of%20growth.%20A%20young%20sea-captain%20from%20a%20New%20England%20village%20on%20a%20long%20and%20lonely%20voyage%20falls%20upon%20a%20copy%20of%20Shelley.%20Appeal%20is%20made%20to%20his%20fine%20but%20untrained%20mind%2C%20and%20the%20book%20of%20the%20boy%20poet%20becomes%20the%20seaman%26%2339%3Bs%20university.%20The%20wide%20world%20of%20poetry%20and%20of%20the%20other%20fine%20arts%20is%20opened%2C%20and%20the%20Shelleyian%20specialist%20becomes%20a%20cultivated%2C%20original%2C%20and%20charming%20man.%20A%20busy%20merchant%20loves%20flowers%2C%20and%20in%20all%20his%20free%20hours%20studies%20them.%20Each%20new%20spring%20adds%20knowledge%20to%20his%20knowledge%2C%20and%20his%20friends%20continually%20bring%20him%20their%20strange%20discoveries.%20With%20growing%20wealth%20he%20cultivates%20rare%20and%20beautiful%20plants%2C%20and%20shares%20them%20with%20his%20fortunate%20acquaintances.%20Happy%20the%20companion%20invited%20to%20a%20walk%20or%20a%20drive%20with%20such%20observant%20eyes%2C%20such%20vivid%20talk!%20Because%20of%20this%20cheerful%20interest%20in%20flowers%2C%20and%20this%20ingenious%20skill%20in%20dealing%20with%20them%2C%20the%20man%20himself%20is%20interesting.%20All%20his%20powers%20are%20alert%2C%20and%20his%20judgment%20is%20valued%20in%20public%20life%20and%20in%20private%20business.%20Or%20is%20it%20more%20exact%20to%20say%20that%20because%20he%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20man%20who%20would%20insist%20upon%20having%20such%20interests%20outside%20his%20daily%20work%2C%20he%20is%20still%20fresh%20and%20young%20and%20capable%20of%20growth%20at%20an%20age%20when%20many%20other%20men%20are%20dull%20and%20old%20and%20certain%20that%20the%20time%20of%20decay%20is%20at%20hand%3F%20There%20are%20two%20reasons%20why%20women%20need%20to%20cultivate%20these%20large%20and%20abiding%20interests%20even%20more%20persistently%20than%20men.%20In%20the%20first%20place%2C%20they%20have%20more%20leisure.%20They%20are%20indeed%20the%20only%20leisure%20class%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20only%20large%20body%20of%20persons%20who%20are%20not%20called%20upon%20to%20win%20their%20daily%20bread%20in%20direct%20wage-earning%20ways.%20As%20yet%2C%20fortunately%2C%20few%20men%20among%20us%20have%20so%20little%20self-respect%20as%20to%20idle%20about%20our%20streets%20and%20drawing-rooms%20because%20their%20fathers%20are%20rich%20enough%20to%20support%20them.%20We%20are%20not%20without%20our%20unemployed%20poor%3B%20but%20roving%20tramps%20and%20idle%20clubmen%20are%20after%20all%20not%20of%20large%20consequence.%20Our%20serious%2C%20non-producing%20classes%20are%20chiefly%20women.%20It%20is%20the%20regular%20ambition%20of%20the%20chivalrous%20American%20to%20make%20all%20the%20women%20who%20depend%20on%20him%20so%20comfortable%20that%20they%20need%20do%20nothing%20for%20themselves.%20Machinery%20has%20taken%20nearly%20all%20the%20former%20occupations%20of%20women%20out%20of%20the%20home%20into%20the%20shop%20and%20factory.%20Widespread%20wealth%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20the%20inherited%20theory%20that%20it%20is%20not%20well%20for%20the%20woman%20to%20earn%20money%20so%20long%20as%20father%20or%20brothers%20can%20support%20her%2C%20have%20brought%20about%20a%20condition%20of%20things%20in%20which%20there%20is%20social%20danger%2C%20unless%20with%20the%20larger%20leisure%20are%20given%20high%20and%20enduring%20interests.%20To%20health%20especially%20there%20is%20great%20danger%2C%20for%20nothing%20breaks%20down%20a%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20health%20like%20idleness%20and%20its%20resulting%20ennui.%20More%20people%2C%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20are%20broken%20down%20nervously%20because%20they%20are%20bored%2C%20than%20because%20they%20are%20overworked%3B%20and%20more%20still%20go%20to%20pieces%20through%20fussiness%2C%20unwholesome%20living%2C%20worry%20over%20petty%20details%2C%20and%20the%20daily%20disappointments%20which%20result%20from%20small%20and%20superficial%20training.%20And%20then%2C%20besides%20the%20danger%20to%20health%2C%20there%20is%20the%20danger%20to%20character.%20I%20need%20not%20dwell%20on%20the%20undermining%20influence%20which%20men%20also%20feel%20when%20occupation%20is%20taken%20away%20and%20no%20absorbing%20private%20interest%20fills%20the%20vacancy.%20The%20vices%20of%20luxurious%20city%20life%20are%20perhaps%20hardly%20more%20destructive%20to%20character%20than%20is%20the%20slow%20deterioration%20of%20barren%20country%20life.%20Though%20the%20conditions%20in%20the%20two%20cases%20are%20exactly%20opposite%2C%20the%20trouble%20is%20often%20the%20same%2C--absence%20of%20noble%20interests.%20In%20the%20city%20restless%20idleness%20organizes%20amusement%3B%20in%20the%20country%20deadly%20dulness%20succeeds%20daily%20toil.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20second%20reason%20why%20a%20girl%20should%20acquire%20for%20herself%20strong%20and%20worthy%20interests.%20The%20regular%20occupations%20of%20women%20in%20their%20homes%20are%20generally%20disconnected%20and%20of%20little%20educational%20value%2C%20at%20least%20as%20those%20homes%20are%20at%20present%20conducted.%20Given%20the%20best%20will%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20daily%20doing%20of%20household%20details%20becomes%20a%20wearisome%20monotony%20if%20the%20mere%20performance%20of%20them%20is%20all.%20To%20make%20drudgery%20divine%20a%20woman%20must%20have%20a%20brain%20to%20plan%20and%20eyes%20to%20see%20how%20to%20%22sweep%20a%20room%20as%20to%20God%26%2339%3Bs%20laws.%22%20Imagination%20and%20knowledge%20should%20be%20the%20hourly%20companions%20of%20her%20who%20would%20make%20a%20fine%20art%20of%20each%20detail%20in%20kitchen%20and%20nursery.%20Too%20long%20has%20the%20pin%20been%20the%20appropriate%20symbol%20of%20the%20average%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20life--the%20pin%2C%20which%20only%20temporarily%20holds%20together%20things%20which%20may%20or%20may%20not%20have%20any%20organic%20connection%20with%20one%20another.%20While%20undoubtedly%20most%20women%20must%20spend%20the%20larger%20part%20of%20life%20in%20this%20modest%20pin-work%2C%20holding%20together%20the%20little%20things%20of%20home%20and%20school%20and%20society%20and%20church%2C%20it%20is%20also%20true%2C%20that%20cohesive%20work%20itself%20cannot%20be%20done%20well%2C%20even%20in%20humble%20circumstances%2C%20except%20by%20the%20refined%2C%20the%20trained%2C%20the%20growing%20woman.%20The%20smallest%20village%2C%20the%20plainest%20home%2C%20give%20ample%20space%20for%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20trained%20college%20woman.%20And%20the%20reason%20why%20such%20homes%20and%20such%20villages%20are%20so%20often%20barren%20of%20grace%20and%20variety%20is%20just%20because%20these%20fine%20qualities%20have%20not%20ruled%20them.%20The%20higher%20graces%20of%20civilization%20halt%20among%20us%3B%20dainty%20and%20finished%20ways%20of%20living%20give%20place%20to%20common%20ways%2C%20while%20vulgar%20tastes%2C%20slatternly%20habits%2C%20clouds%20and%20despondency%20reign%20in%20the%20house.%20Little%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20die%20in%20needless%20thousands%20because%20of%20the%20dull%2C%20unimaginative%20women%20on%20whom%20they%20depend.%20Such%20women%20have%20been%20satisfied%20with%20just%20getting%20along%2C%20instead%20of%20packing%20everything%20they%20do%20with%20brains%2C%20instead%20of%20studying%20the%20best%20possible%20way%20of%20doing%20everything%20small%20or%20large%3B%20for%20there%20is%20always%20a%20best%20way%2C%20whether%20of%20setting%20a%20table%2C%20of%20trimming%20a%20hat%2C%20or%20teaching%20a%20child%20to%20read.%20And%20this%20taste%20for%20perfection%20can%20be%20cultivated%3B%20indeed%2C%20it%20must%20be%20cultivated%2C%20if%20our%20standards%20of%20living%20are%20to%20be%20raised.%20There%20is%20now%20scientific%20knowledge%20enough%2C%20there%20is%20money%20enough%2C%20to%20prevent%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20evils%20which%20afflict%20our%20social%20organism%2C%20if%20mere%20knowledge%20or%20wealth%20could%20avail%3B%20but%20the%20greater%20difficulty%20is%20to%20make%20intelligence%2C%20character%2C%20good%20taste%2C%20unselfishness%20prevail.%20What%2C%20then%2C%20are%20the%20interests%20which%20powerfully%20appeal%20to%20mind%20and%20heart%2C%20and%20so%20are%20fitted%20to%20become%20the%20strengthening%20companions%20of%20a%20woman%26%2339%3Bs%20life%3F%20I%20shall%20mention%20only%20three%2C%20all%20of%20them%20such%20as%20are%20elaborately%20fostered%20by%20college%20life.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20love%20of%20great%20literature.%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20that%20use%20of%20books%20by%20which%20a%20man%20may%20get%20what%20is%20called%20a%20good%20education%20and%20so%20be%20better%20qualified%20for%20the%20battle%20of%20life%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20mention%20books%20in%20their%20character%20as%20reservoirs%20of%20knowledge%2C%20books%20which%20we%20need%20for%20special%20purposes%2C%20and%20which%20are%20no%20longer%20of%20consequence%20when%20our%20purpose%20with%20them%20is%20served.%20I%20have%20in%20mind%20the%20great%20books%2C%20especially%20the%20great%20poets%2C%20books%20to%20be%20adopted%20as%20a%20resource%20and%20a%20solace.%20The%20chief%20reason%20why%20so%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20how%20to%20make%20comrades%20of%20such%20books%20is%20because%20they%20have%20come%20to%20them%20too%20late.%20We%20have%20in%20this%20country%20enormous%20numbers%20of%20readers%2C%20probably%20a%20larger%20number%20who%20read%2C%20and%20who%20read%20many%20hours%20in%20the%20week%2C%20than%20has%20ever%20been%20known%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20what%20do%20these%20millions%20read%20besides%20the%20newspapers%3F%20Possibly%20a%20denominational%20religious%20weekly%20and%20another%20journal%20of%20fashion%20or%20business.%20Then%20come%20the%20thousands%20who%20read%20the%20best%20magazines%2C%20and%20whatever%20else%20is%20for%20the%20moment%20popular%20in%20novels%20and%20poetry--the%20last%20dialect%20story%2C%20the%20fashionable%20poem%2C%20the%20questionable%20but%20talked-of%20novel.%20Let%20a%20violent%20attack%20be%20made%20on%20the%20decency%20of%20a%20new%20story%20and%20instantly%2C%20if%20only%20it%20is%20clever%2C%20its%20author%20becomes%20famous.%20But%20the%20fashions%20in%20reading%20of%20a%20restless%20race--the%20women%20too%20idle%2C%20the%20men%20too%20heavily%20worked--I%20will%20not%20discuss%20here.%20Let%20light%20literature%20be%20devourered%20by%20our%20populace%20as%20his%20drug%20is%20taken%20by%20the%20opium-eater%2C%20and%20with%20a%20similar%20narcotic%20effect.%20We%20can%20only%20seek%20out%20the%20children%2C%20and%20hope%20by%20giving%20them%20from%20babyhood%20bits%20of%20the%20noblest%20literature%2C%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20great%20opportunities%20of%20mature%20life.%20I%20urge%2C%20therefore%2C%20reading%20as%20a%20mental%20stimulus%2C%20as%20a%20solace%20in%20trouble%2C%20a%20perpetual%20source%20of%20delight%3B%20and%20I%20would%20point%20out%20that%20we%20must%20not%20delay%20to%20make%20the%20great%20friendships%20that%20await%20us%20on%20the%20library%20shelves%20until%20sickness%20shuts%20the%20door%20on%20the%20outer%20world%2C%20or%20death%20enters%20the%20home%20and%20silences%20the%20voices%20that%20once%20helped%20to%20make%20these%20friendships%20sweet.%20If%20Homer%20and%20Shakespeare%20and%20Wordsworth%20and%20Browning%20are%20to%20have%20meaning%20for%20us%20when%20we%20need%20them%20most%2C%20it%20will%20be%20because%20they%20come%20to%20us%20as%20old%20familiar%20friends%20whose%20influences%20have%20permeated%20the%20glad%20and%20busy%20days%20before.%20The%20last%20time%20I%20heard%20James%20Russell%20Lowell%20talk%20to%20college%20girls%2C%20he%20said%2C--for%20he%20was%20too%20ill%20to%20say%20many%20words--%22I%20have%20only%20this%20one%20message%20to%20leave%20with%20you.%20In%20all%20your%20work%20in%20college%20never%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20you%20have%20come%20here.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20you%20may%20get%20something%20by%20which%20to%20earn%20your%20bread%2C%20but%20that%20every%20mouthful%20of%20bread%20may%20be%20the%20sweeter%20to%20your%20taste.%22%20And%20this%20is%20the%20power%20possessed%20by%20the%20mighty%20dead%2C--men%20of%20every%20time%20and%20nation%2C%20whose%20voices%20death%20cannot%20silence%2C%20who%20are%20waiting%20even%20at%20the%20poor%20man%26%2339%3Bs%20elbow%2C%20whose%20illuminating%20words%20may%20be%20had%20for%20the%20price%20of%20a%20day%26%2339%3Bs%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen%20or%20the%20street%2C%20for%20lack%20of%20love%20of%20whom%20many%20a%20luxurious%20home%20is%20a%20dull%20and%20solitary%20spot%2C%20breeding%20misery%20and%20vice.%20Now%20the%20modern%20college%20is%20especially%20equipped%20to%20introduce%20its%20students%20to%20such%20literature.%20The%20library%20is%20at%20last%20understood%20to%20be%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20college.%20The%20modern%20librarian%20is%20not%20the%20keeper%20of%20books%2C%20as%20was%20his%20predecessor%2C%20but%20the%20distributer%20of%20them%2C%20and%20the%20guide%20to%20their%20resources%2C%20proud%20when%20he%20increases%20the%20use%20of%20his%20treasures.%20Every%20language%2C%20ancient%20or%20modern%2C%20which%20contains%20a%20literature%20is%20now%20taught%20in%20college.%20Its%20history%20is%20examined%2C%20its%20philology%2C%20its%20masterpieces%2C%20and%20more%20than%20ever%20is%20English%20literature%20studied%20and%20loved.%20There%20is%20now%20every%20opportunity%20for%20the%20college%20student%20to%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20use%20of%20his%20own%20tongue%20and%20pen.%20What%20other%20men%20painfully%20strive%20for%20he%20can%20enjoy%20to%20the%20full%20with%20comparatively%20little%20effort.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20second%20invigorating%20interest%20to%20which%20college%20training%20introduces%20its%20student.%20I%20mean%20the%20study%20of%20nature%2C%20intimacy%20with%20the%20strange%20and%20beautiful%20world%20in%20which%20we%20live.%20%22Nature%20never%20did%20betray%20the%20heart%20that%20loved%20her%2C%22%20sang%20her%20poet%20high%20priest.%20When%20the%20world%20has%20been%20too%20much%20with%20us%2C%20nothing%20else%20is%20so%20refreshing%20to%20tired%20eyes%20and%20mind%20as%20woods%20and%20water%2C%20and%20an%20intelligent%20knowledge%20of%20the%20life%20within%20them.%20For%20a%20generation%20past%20there%20has%20been%20a%20well-nigh%20universal%20turning%20of%20the%20population%20toward%20the%20cities.%20In%201840%20only%20nine%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20people%20lived%20in%20cities%20of%208%2C000%20inhabitants%20or%20more.%20Now%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20us%20are%20found%20in%20cities.%20But%20the%20electric-car%2C%20the%20telephone%2C%20the%20bicycle%2C%20still%20keep%20avenues%20to%20the%20country%20open.%20Certain%20it%20is%20that%20city%20people%20feel%20a%20growing%20hunger%20for%20the%20country%2C%20particularly%20when%20grass%20begins%20to%20grow.%20This%20is%20a%20healthy%20taste%2C%20and%20must%20increase%20the%20general%20knowledge%20and%20love%20of%20nature.%20Fortunate%20are%20the%20little%20children%20in%20those%20schools%20whose%20teachers%20know%20and%20love%20the%20world%20in%20which%20they%20live.%20Their%20young%20eyes%20are%20early%20opened%20to%20the%20beauty%20of%20birds%20and%20trees%20and%20plants.%20Not%20only%20should%20we%20expect%20our%20girls%20to%20have%20a%20feeling%20for%20the%20fine%20sunset%20or%20the%20wide-reaching%20panorama%20of%20field%20and%20water%2C%20but%20to%20know%20something%20also%20about%20the%20less%20obvious%20aspects%20of%20nature%2C%20its%20structure%2C%20its%20methods%20of%20work%2C%20and%20the%20endless%20diversity%20of%20its%20parts.%20No%20one%20can%20have%20read%20Matthew%20Arnold%26%2339%3Bs%20letters%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20his%20sister%2C%20without%20being%20struck%20by%20the%20immense%20enjoyment%20he%20took%20throughout%20his%20singularly%20simple%20and%20hard-working%20life%20in%20flowers%20and%20trees%20and%20rivers.%20The%20English%20lake%20country%20had%20given%20him%20this%20happy%20inheritance%2C%20with%20everywhere%20its%20sound%20of%20running%20water%20and%20its%20wealth%20of%20greenery.%20There%20is%20a%20close%20connection%20between%20the%20marvellous%20unbroken%20line%20of%20English%20song%2C%20and%20the%20passionate%20love%20of%20the%20Englishman%20for%20a%20home%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20birds%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20green%20fields.%20%22The%20world%20is%20so%20full%20of%20a%20number%20of%20things%2C%20That%20I%20think%20we%20should%20all%20be%20as%20happy%20as%20kings%2C%22%20is%20the%20opinion%20of%20everybody%20who%20knows%20nature%20as%20did%20Robert%20Louis%20Stevenson.%20And%20so%20our%20college%20student%20may%20begin%20to%20know%20it.%20Let%20her%20enter%20the%20laboratories%20and%20investigate%20for%20herself.%20Let%20her%20make%20her%20delicate%20experiments%20with%20the%20blowpipe%20or%20the%20balance%3B%20let%20her%20track%20mysterious%20life%20from%20one%20hiding-place%20to%20another%3B%20let%20her%20%22name%20all%20the%20birds%20without%20a%20gun%2C%22%20and%20make%20intimates%20of%20flower%20and%20fish%20and%20butterfly--and%20she%20is%20dull%20indeed%20if%20breezy%20tastes%20do%20not%20follow%20her%20through%20life%2C%20and%20forbid%20any%20of%20her%20days%20to%20be%20empty%20of%20intelligent%20enjoyment.%20%22Keep%20your%20years%20beautiful%3B%20make%20your%20own%20atmosphere%2C%22%20was%20the%20parting%20advice%20of%20my%20college%20president%2C%20himself%20a%20living%20illustration%20of%20what%20he%20said.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20short%20step%20from%20the%20love%20of%20the%20complex%20and%20engaging%20world%20in%20which%20we%20live%20to%20the%20love%20of%20our%20comrades%20in%20it.%20Accordingly%20the%20third%20precious%20interest%20to%20be%20cultivated%20by%20the%20college%20student%20is%20an%20interest%20in%20people.%20The%20scholar%20today%20is%20not%20a%20being%20who%20dwells%20apart%20in%20his%20cloister%2C%20the%20monk%26%2339%3Bs%20successor%3B%20he%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20thoughts%20and%20