ent%20in%20manners%2C%20faults%20which%20are%20as%20ruinous%20as%20vices.%22%20The%20supreme%20end%20of%20college%20training%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%22is%20usefulness%20in%20after%20life.%22%20Similarly%2C%20when%20the%20city%20of%20Cambridge%20celebrated%20in%20Harvard%26%2339%3Bs%20Memorial%20Hall%20the%20life%20and%20death%20of%20the%20gallant%20young%20ex-governor%20of%20Massachusetts%2C%20William%20E.%20Russell%2C%20men%20did%20well%20to%20hang%20above%20his%20portrait%20some%20wise%20words%20he%20has%20lately%20said%2C%20%22Never%20forget%20the%20everlasting%20difference%20between%20making%20a%20living%20and%20making%20a%20life.%22%20That%20he%20himself%20never%20forgot%3B%20and%20it%20was%20well%20to%20remind%20citizens%20and%20students%20of%20it%2C%20as%20they%20stood%20there%20facing%20too%20the%20ancient%20words%20all%20Harvard%20men%20face%20when%20they%20take%20their%20college%20degrees%20and%20go%20out%20into%20the%20world%2C%20%22They%20that%20be%20wise%20shall%20shine%20as%20the%20brightness%20of%20the%20firmament%2C%20and%20they%20that%20turn%20many%20to%20righteousness%20as%20the%20stars%20for%20ever%20and%20ever.%22%20Good%20words%20these%20to%20go%20out%20from%20college%20with.%20The%20girls%20of%20Wellesley%20gather%20every%20morning%20at%20chapel%20to%20bow%20their%20heads%20together%20for%20a%20moment%20before%20they%20scatter%20among%20the%20libraries%20and%20lecture-rooms%20and%20begin%20the%20experiments%20of%20the%20new%20day.%20And%20always%20their%20college%20motto%20meets%20the%20eyes%20that%20are%20raised%20to%20its%20penetrating%20message%2C%20%22Not%20to%20be%20ministered%20unto%2C%20but%20to%20minister.%22%20How%20many%20a%20young%20heart%20has%20loyally%20responded%2C%20%22And%20to%20give%20life%20a%20ransom%20for%20many.%22%20That%20is%20the%20%22Wellesley%20spirit%3B%22%20and%20the%20same%20sweet%20spirit%20of%20devout%20service%20has%20gone%20forth%20from%20all%20our%20college%20halls.%20In%20any%20of%20them%20one%20may%20catch%20th