20and%20any%20volunteers%20associated%20with%20the%20production%2C%20promotion%20and%20distribution%20of%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20electronic%20works%2C%20harmless%20from%20all%20liability%2C%20costs%20and%20expenses%2C%20including%20legal%20fees%2C%20that%20arise%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20from%20any%20of%20the%20following%20which%20you%20do%20or%20cause%20to%20occur%3A%20(a)%20distribution%20of%20this%20or%20any%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20work%2C%20(b)%20alteration%2C%20modification%2C%20or%20additions%20or%20deletions%20to%20any%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20work%2C%20and%20(c)%20any%20Defect%20you%20cause.%20Section%202.%20Information%20about%20the%20Mission%20of%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20is%20synonymous%20with%20the%20free%20distribution%20of%20electronic%20works%20in%20formats%20readable%20by%20the%20widest%20variety%20of%20computers%20including%20obsolete%2C%20old%2C%20middle-aged%20and%20new%20computers.%20It%20exists%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20hundreds%20of%20volunteers%20and%20donations%20from%20people%20in%20all%20walks%20of%20life.%20Volunteers%20and%20financial%20support%20to%20provide%20volunteers%20with%20the%20assistance%20they%20need%2C%20is%20critical%20to%20reaching%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%26%2339%3Bs%20goals%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20collection%20will%20remain%20freely%20available%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%20In%202001%2C%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20was%20created%20to%20provide%20a%20secure%20and%20permanent%20future%20for%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20and%20future%20generations.%20To%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20and%20how%20your%20efforts%20and%20donations%20can%20help%2C%20see%20Sections%203%20and%204%20and%20the%20Foundation%20web%20page%20at%20http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pglaf.org.%20Section%203.%20Information%20about%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20The%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20is%20a%20non%20profit%20501(c)(3)%20educational%20corporation%20organized%20under%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Mississippi%20and%20granted%20tax%20exempt%20status%20by%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service.%20The%20Foundation%26%2339%3Bs%20EIN%20or%20federal%20tax%20identification%20number%20is%2064-6221541.%20Its%20501(c)(3)%20letter%20is%20posted%20at%20http%3A%2F%2Fpglaf.org%2Ffundraising.%20Contributions%20to%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20are%20tax%20deductible%20to%20the%20full%20extent%20permitted%20by%20U.S.%20federal%20laws%20and%20your%20state%26%2339%3Bs%20laws.%20The%20Foundation%26%2339%3Bs%20principal%20office%20is%20located%20at%204557%20Melan%20Dr.%20S.%20Fairbanks%2C%20AK%2C%2099712.%2C%20but%20its%20volunteers%20and%20employees%20are%20scattered%20throughout%20numerous%20locations.%20Its%20business%20office%20is%20located%20at%20809%20North%201500%20West%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20UT%2084116%2C%20(801)%20596-1887%2C%20email%20business%40pglaf.org.%20Email%20contact%20links%20and%20up%20to%20date%20contact%20information%20can%20be%20found%20at%20the%20Foundation%26%2339%3Bs%20web%20site%20and%20official%20page%20at%20http%3A%2F%2Fpglaf.org%20For%20additional%20contact%20information%3A%20Dr.%20Gregory%20B.%20Newby%20Chief%20Executive%20and%20Director%20gbnewby%40pglaf.org%20Section%204.%20Information%20about%20Donations%20to%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20depends%20upon%20and%20cannot%20survive%20without%20wide%20spread%20public%20support%20and%20donations%20to%20carry%20out%20its%20mission%20of%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20public%20domain%20and%20licensed%20works%20that%20can%20be%20freely%20distributed%20in%20machine%20readable%20form%20accessible%20by%20the%20widest%20array%20of%20equipment%20including%20outdated%20equipment.%20Many%20small%20donations%20(%241%20to%20%245%2C000)%20are%20particularly%20important%20to%20maintaining%20tax%20exempt%20status%20with%20the%20IRS.%20The%20Foundation%20is%20committed%20to%20complying%20with%20the%20laws%20regulating%20charities%20and%20charitable%20donations%20in%20all%2050%20states%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20Compliance%20requirements%20are%20not%20uniform%20and%20it%20takes%20a%20considerable%20effort%2C%20much%20paperwork%20and%20many%20fees%20to%20meet%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20these%20requirements.%20We%20do%20not%20solicit%20donations%20in%20locations%20where%20we%20have%20not%20received%20written%20confirmation%20of%20compliance.%20To%20SEND%20DONATIONS%20or%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20compliance%20for%20any%20particular%20state%20visit%20http%3A%2F%2Fpglaf.org%20While%20we%20cannot%20and%20do%20not%20solicit%20contributions%20from%20states%20where%20we%20have%20not%20met%20the%20solicitation%20requirements%2C%20we%20know%20of%20no%20prohibition%20against%20accepting%20unsolicited%20donations%20from%20donors%20in%20such%20states%20who%20approach%20us%20with%20offers%20to%20donate.%20International%20donations%20are%20gratefully%20accepted%2C%20but%20we%20cannot%20make%20any%20statements%20concerning%20tax%20treatment%20of%20donations%20received%20from%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%20U.S.%20laws%20alone%20swamp%20our%20small%20staff.%20Please%20check%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Web%20pages%20for%20current%20donation%20methods%20and%20addresses.%20Donations%20are%20accepted%20in%20a%20number%20of%20other%20ways%20including%20including%20checks%2C%20online%20payments%20and%20credit%20card%20donations.%20To%20donate%2C%20please%20visit%3A%20http%3A%2F%2Fpglaf.org%2Fdonate%20Section%205.%20General%20Information%20About%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20electronic%20works.%20Professor%20Michael%20S.%20Hart%20is%20the%20originator%20of%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20concept%20of%20a%20library%20of%20electronic%20works%20that%20could%20be%20freely%20shared%20with%20anyone.%20For%20thirty%20years%2C%20he%20produced%20and%20distributed%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20eBooks%20with%20only%20a%20loose%20network%20of%20volunteer%20support.%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%20eBooks%20are%20often%20created%20from%20several%20printed%20editions%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20confirmed%20as%20Public%20Domain%20in%20the%20U.S.%20unless%20a%20copyright%20notice%20is%20included.%20Thus%2C%20we%20do%20not%20necessarily%20keep%20eBooks%20in%20compliance%20with%20any%20particular%20paper%20edition.%20Most%20people%20start%20at%20our%20Web%20site%20which%20has%20the%20main%20PG%20search%20facility%3A%20http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gutenberg.net%20This%20Web%20site%20includes%20information%20about%20Project%20Gutenberg-tm%2C%20including%20how%20to%20make%20donations%20to%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20Literary%20Archive%20Foundation%2C%20how%20to%20help%20produce%20our%20new%20eBooks%2C%20and%20how%20to%20subscribe%20to%20our%20email%20newsletter%20to%20hear%20about%20new%20eBooks.%20http%3A%2F%2Fbytesizematters.com%2F%20Project%20Gutenberg%26%2339%3Bs%20Why%20go%20to%20College%3F%20an%20Address%2C%20by%20Alice%20Freeman%20Palmer%20This%20eBook%20is%20for%20the%20use%20of%20anyone%20anywhere%20at%20no%20cost%20and%20with%20almost%20no%20restrictions%20whatsoever.%20You%20may%20copy%20it%2C%20give%20it%20away%20or%20re-use%20it%20under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20Project%20Gutenberg%20License%20included%20with%20this%20eBook%20or%20online%20at%20www.gutenberg.net%20Title%3A%20Why%20go%20to%20College%3F%20an%20Address%20Author%3A%20Alice%20Freeman%20Palmer%20Posting%20Date%3A%20November%205%2C%202008%20%5BEBook%20%232361%5D%20Release%20Date%3A%20October%2C%202000%20Language%3A%20English%20Character%20set%20encoding%3A%20ASCII%20***%20START%20OF%20THIS%20PROJECT%20GUTENBERG%20EBOOK%20WHY%20GO%20TO%20COLLEGE%3F%20AN%20ADDRESS%20***%20Produced%20by%20Stephanie%20L.%20Johnson.%20HTML%20version%20by%20Al%20Haines.%20WHY%20GO%20TO%20COLLEGE%3F%20an%20Address%20BY%20ALICE%20FREEMAN%20PALMER%20Formerly%20President%20of%20Wellesley%20College%20To%20a%20largely%20increasing%20number%20of%20young%20girls%20college%20doors%20are%20opening%20every%20year.%20Every%20year%20adds%20to%20the%20number%20of%20men%20who%20feel%20as%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20a%20successful%20lawyer%20in%20a%20great%20city%2C%20felt%20when%20in%20talking%20of%20the%20future%20of%20his%20four%20little%20children%20he%20said%2C%20%22For%20the%20two%20boys%20it%20is%20not%20so%20serious%2C%20but%20I%20lie%20down%20at%20night%20afraid%20to%20die%20and%20leave%20my%20daughters%20only%20a%20bank%20account.%22%20Year%20by%20year%2C%20too%2C%20the%20experiences%20of%20life%20are%20teaching%20mothers%20that%20happiness%20does%20not%20necessarily%20come%20to%20their%20daughters%20when%20accounts%20are%20large%20and%20banks%20are%20sound%2C%20but%20that%20on%20the%20contrary%20they%20take%20grave%20risks%20when%20they%20trust%20everything%20to%20accumulated%20wealth%20and%20the%20chance%20of%20a%20happy%20marriage.%20Our%20American%20girls%20themselves%20are%20becoming%20aware%20that%20they%20need%20the%20stimulus%2C%20the%20discipline%2C%20the%20knowledge%2C%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20college%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20school%2C%20if%20they%20are%20to%20prepare%20themselves%20for%20the%20most%20serviceable%20lives.%20But%20there%20are%20still%20parents%20who%20say%2C%20%22There%20is%20no%20need%20that%20my%20daughter%20should%20teach%3B%20then%20why%20should%20she%20go%20to%20college%3F%22%20I%20will%20not%20reply%20that%20college%20training%20is%20a%20life%20insurance%20for%20a%20girl%2C%20a%20pledge%20that%20she%20possesses%20the%20disciplined%20ability%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20for%20herself%20and%20others%20in%20case%20of%20need%2C%20for%20I%20prefer%20to%20insist%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20giving%20every%20girl%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20her%20present%20circumstances%2C%20a%20special%20training%20in%20some%20one%20thing%20by%20which%20she%20can%20render%20society%20service%2C%20not%20amateur%20but%20of%20an%20expert%20sort%2C%20and%20service%20too%20for%20which%20it%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20price.%20The%20number%20of%20families%20will%20surely%20increase%20who%20will%20follow%20the%20example%20of%20an%20eminent%20banker%20whose%20daughters%20have%20been%20given%20each%20her%20specialty.%20One%20has%20chosen%20music%2C%20and%20has%20gone%20far%20with%20the%20best%20masters%20in%20this%20country%20and%20in%20Europe%2C%20so%20far%20that%20she%20now%20holds%20a%20high%20rank%20among%20musicians%20at%20home%20and%20abroad.%20Another%20has%20taken%20art%2C%20and%20has%20not%20been%20content%20to%20paint%20pretty%20gifts%20for%20her%20friends%2C%20but%20in%20the%20studios%20of%20New%20York%2C%20Munich%2C%20and%20Paris%2C%20she%20has%20won%20the%20right%20to%20be%20called%20an%20artist%2C%20and%20in%20her%20studio%20at%20home%20to%20paint%20portraits%20which%20have%20a%20market%20value.%20A%20third%20has%20proved%20that%20she%20can%20earn%20her%20living%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20by%20her%20exquisite%20jellies%2C%20preserves%2C%20and%20sweetmeats.%20Yet%20the%20house%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20the%20house%20by%20the%20sea%2C%20and%20the%20friends%20in%20the%20city%20are%20not%20neglected%2C%20nor%20are%20these%20young%20women%20found%20less%20attractive%20because%20of%20their%20special%20accomplishments.%20While%20it%20is%20not%20true%20that%20all%20girls%20should%20go%20to%20college%20any%20more%20than%20that%20all%20boys%20should%20go%2C%20it%20is%20nevertheless%20true%20that%20they%20should%20go%20in%20greater%20numbers%20than%20at%20present.%20They%20fail%20to%20go%20because%20they%2C%20their%20parents%20and%20their%20teachers%2C%20do%20not%20see%20clearly%20the%20personal%20benefits%20distinct%20from%20the%20commercial%20value%20of%20a%20college%20training.%20I%20wish%20here%20to%20discuss%20these%20benefits%2C%20these%20larger%20gifts%20of%20the%20college%20life%2C--what%20they%20may%20be%2C%20and%20for%20whom%20they%20are%20waiting.%20It%20is%20undoubtedly%20true%20that%20many%20girls%20are%20totally%20unfitted%20by%20home%20and%20school%20life%20for%20a%20valuable%20college%20course.%20These%20joys%20and%20successes%2C%20these%20high%20interests%20and%20friendships%2C%20are%20not%20for%20the%20self-conscious%20and%20nervous%20invalid%2C%20nor%20for%20her%20who%20in%20the%20exuberance%20of%20youth%20recklessly%20ignores%20the%20laws%20of%20a%20healthy%20life.%20The%20good%20society%20of%20scholars%20and%20of%20libraries%20and%20laboratories%20has%20no%20place%20and%20no%20attraction%20for%20her%20who%20finds%20no%20message%20in%20Plato%2C%20no%20beauty%20in%20mathematical%20order%2C%20and%20who%20never%20longs%20to%20know%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20stars%20over%20her%20head%20or%20the%20flowers%20under%20her%20feet.%20Neither%20will%20the%20finer%20opportunities%20of%20college%20life%20appeal%20to%20one%20who%2C%20until%20she%20is%20eighteen%20(is%20there%20such%20a%20girl%20in%20this%20country%3F)%2C%20has%20felt%20no%20passion%20for%20the%20service%20of%20others%2C%20no%20desire%20to%20know%20if%20through%20history%20or%20philosophy%2C%20or%20any%20study%20of%20the%20laws%20of%20society%2C%20she%20can%20learn%20why%20the%20world%20is%20so%20sad%2C%20so%20hard%2C%20so%20selfish%20as%20she%20finds%20it%2C%20even%20when%20she%20looks%20upon%20it%20from%20the%20most%20sheltered%20life.%20No%2C%20the%20college%20cannot%20be%2C%20should%20not%20try%20to%20be%2C%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20hospital%2C%20reformatory%20or%20kindergarten.%20To%20do%20its%20best%20work%20it%20should%20be%20organized%20for%20the%20strong%2C%20not%20for%20the%20weak%3B%20for%20the%20high-minded%2C%20self-controlled%2C%20generous%2C%20and%20courageous%20spirits%2C%20not%20for%20the%20indifferent%2C%20the%20dull%2C%20the%20idle%2C%20or%20those%20who%20are%20already%20forming%20their%20characters%20on%20the%20amusement%20theory%20of%20life.%20All%20these%20perverted%20young%20people%20may%2C%20and%20often%20do%2C%20get%20large%20benefit%20and%20invigoration%2C%20new%20ideals%2C%20and%20unselfish%20purposes%20from%20their%20four%20years%26%2339%3B%20companionship%20with%20teachers%20and%20comrades%20of%20a%20higher%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20and%20moral%20stature%20than%20their%20own.%20I%20have%20seen%20girls%20change%20so%20much%20in%20college%20that%20I%20have%20wondered%20if%20their%20friends%20at%20home%20would%20know%20them%2C--the%20voice%2C%20the%20carriage%2C%20the%20unconscious%20manner%2C%20all%20telling%20a%20story%20of%20new%20tastes%20and%20habits%20and%20loves%20and%20interests%2C%20that%20had%20wrought%20out%20in%20very%20truth%20a%20new%20creature.%20Yet%20in%20spite%20of%20this%20I%20have%20sometimes%20thought%20that%20in%20college%20more%20than%20elsewhere%20the%20old%20law%20holds%2C%20%22To%20him%20that%20hath%20shall%20be%20given%20and%20he%20shall%20have%20abundance%2C%20but%20from%20him%20who%20hath%20not%20shall%20be%20taken%20away%20even%20that%20which%20he%20seemeth%20to%20have.%22%20For%20it%20is%20the%20young%20life%20which%20is%20open%20and%20prepared%20to%20receive%20which%20obtains%20the%20gracious%20and%20uplifting%20influences%20of%20college%20days.%20What%2C%20then%2C%20for%20such%20persons%20are%20the%20rich%20and%20abiding%20rewards%20of%20study%20in%20college%20or%20university%3F%20Pre-eminently%20the%20college%20is%20a%20place%20of%20education.%20That%20is%20the%20ground%20of%20its%20being.%20We%20go%20to%20college%20to%20know%2C%20assured%20that%20knowledge%20is%20sweet%20and%20powerful%2C%20that%20a%20good%20education%20emancipates%20the%20mind%20and%20makes%20us%20citizens%20of%20the%20world.%20No%20college%20which%20does%20not%20thoroughly%20educate%20can%20be%20called%20good%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20else%20it%20does.%20No%20student%20who%20fails%20to%20get%20a%20little%20knowledge%20on%20many%20subjects%2C%20and%20much%20knowledge%20on%20some%2C%20can%20be%20said%20to%20have%20succeeded%2C%20whatever%20other%20advantages%20she%20may%20have%20found%20by%20the%20way.%20It%20is%20a%20beautiful%20and%20significant%20fact%20that%20in%20all%20times%20the%20years%20of%20learning%20have%20been%20also%20the%20years%20of%20romance.%20Those%20who%20love%20girls%20and%20boys%20pray%20that%20our%20colleges%20may%20be%20homes%20of%20sound%20learning%2C%20for%20knowledge%20is%20the%20condition%20of%20every%20college%20blessing.%20%22Let%20no%20man%20incapable%20of%20mathematics%20enter%20here%2C%22%20Plato%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20inscribed%20over%20his%20Academy%20door.%20%22Let%20no%20one%20to%20whom%20hard%20study%20is%20repulsive%20hope%20for%20anything%20from%20us%2C%22%20American%20colleges%20might%20paraphrase.%20Accordingly%20in%20my%20talk%20today%20I%20shall%20say%20little%20of%20the%20direct%20benefits%20of%20knowledge%20which%20the%20college%20affords.%20These%20may%20be%20assumed.%20It%20is%20on%20their%20account%20that%20one%20knocks%20at%20the%20college%20door.%20But%20seeking%20this%20first%2C%20a%20good%20many%20other%20things%20are%20added.%20I%20want%20to%20point%20out%20some%20of%20these%20collateral%20advantages%20of%20going%20to%20college%2C%20or%20rather%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20some%20of%20the%20many%20forms%20in%20which%20the%20winning%20of%20knowledge%20presents%20itself.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20happiness.%20Everybody%20wants%20%22a%20good%20time%2C%22%20especially%20every%20girl%20in%20her%20teens.%20A%20good%20time%2C%20it%20is%20true%2C%20does%20not%20always%20in%20these%20years%20mean%20what%20it%20will%20mean%20by%20and%20by%2C%20any%20more%20than%20the%20girl%20of%20eighteen%20plays%20with%20the%20doll%20which%20entranced%20the%20child%20of%20eight.%20It%20takes%20some%20time%20to%20discover%20that%20work%20is%20the%20best%20sort%20of%20play%2C%20and%20some%20people%20never%20discover%20it%20at%20all.%20But%20when%20mothers%20ask%20such%20questions%20as%20these%3A%20%22How%20can%20I%20make%20my%20daughter%20happy%3F%22%20%22How%20can%20I%20give%20her%20the%20best%20society%3F%22%20%22How%20can%20she%20have%20a%20good%20time%3F%22%20the%20answer%20in%20most%20cases%20is%20simple.%20Send%20her%20to%20college%2C--to%20almost%20any%20college.%20Send%20her%20because%20there%20is%20no%20other%20place%20where%20between%20eighteen%20and%20twenty-two%20she%20is%20so%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20genuinely%20good%20time.%20Merely%20for%20good%20times%2C%20for%20romance%2C%20for%20society%2C%20college%20life%20offers%20unequalled%20opportunities.%20Of%20course%20no%20idle%20person%20can%20possibly%20be%20happy%2C%20even%20for%20a%20day%2C%20nor%20she%20who%20makes%20a%20business%20of%20trying%20to%20amuse%20herself.%20For%20full%20happiness%2C%20though%20its%20springs%20are%20within%2C%20we%20want%20health%20and%20friends%20and%20work%20and%20objects%20of%20aspiration.%20%22We%20live%20by%20admiration%2C%20hope%2C%20and%20love%2C%22%20says%20Wordsworth.%20The%20college%20abounds%20in%20all%20three.%20In%20the%20college%20time%20new%20powers%20are%20sprouting%2C%20and%20intelligence%2C%20merriment%2C%20truthfulness%20and%20generosity%20are%20more%20natural%20than%20the%20opposite%20qualities%20often%20become%20in%20later%20years.%20An%20exhilarating%20atmosphere%20pervades%20the%20place.%20We%20who%20are%20in%20it%20all%20the%20time%20feel%20that%20we%20live%20at%20the%20fountain%20of%20perpetual%20youth%2C%20and%20those%20who%20take%20but%20a%20four%20years%26%2339%3B%20bath%20in%20it%20become%20more%20cheerful%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20full%20of%20promise%20than%20they%20are%20ever%20likely%20to%20find%20themselves%20again%3B%20for%20a%20college%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20compendium%20of%20the%20things%20that%20most%20men%20long%20for.%20It%20is%20usually%20planted%20in%20a%20beautiful%20spot%2C%20the%20charm%20of%20trees%20and%20water%20being%20added%20to%20stately%20buildings%20and%20stimulating%20works%20of%20art.%20Venerable%20associations%20of%20the%20past%20hallow%20its%20halls.%20Leaders%20in%20the%20stirring%20world%20of%20to-day%20return%20at%20each%20commencement%20to%20share%20the%20fresh%20life%20of%20the%20new%20class.%20Books%2C%20pictures%2C%20music%2C%20collections%2C%20appliances%20in%20every%20field%2C%20learned%20teachers%2C%20mirthful%20friends%2C%20athletics%20for%20holidays%2C%20the%20best%20words%20of%20the%20best%20men%20for%20holy%20days%2C--all%20are%20here.%20No%20wonder%20that%20men%20look%20back%20upon%20their%20college%20life%20as%20upon%20halcyon%20days%2C%20the%20romantic%20period%20of%20youth.%20No%20wonder%20that%20Dr.%20Holmes%26%2339%3Bs%20poems%20to%20his%20Harvard%20classmates%20find%20an%20echo%20in%20college%20reunions%20everywhere%3B%20and%20gray-haired%20men%2C%20who%20outside%20the%20narrowing%20circle%20of%20home%20have%20not%20heard%20their%20first%20names%20for%20years%2C%20remain%20Bill%20and%20Joe%20and%20John%20and%20George%20to%20college%20comrades%2C%20even%20if%20unseen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20generation.%20Yet%20a%20girl%20should%20go%20to%20college%20not%20merely%20to%20obtain%20four%20happy%20years%20but%20to%20make%20a%20second%20gain%2C%20which%20is%20often%20overlooked%2C%20and%20is%20little%20understood%20even%20when%20perceived%3B%20I%20mean%20a%20gain%20in%20health.%20The%20old%20notion%20that%20low%20vitality%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20course%20with%20women%3B%20that%20to%20be%20delicate%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20superior%20refinement%2C%20especially%20in%20well-to-do%20families%3B%20that%20sickness%20is%20a%20dispensation%20of%20Providence%2C--these%20notions%20meet%20with%20no%20acceptance%20in%20college.%20Years%20ago%20I%20saw%20in%20the%20mirror%20frame%20of%20a%20college%20freshman%26%2339%3Bs%20room%20this%20little%20formula%3A%20%22Sickness%20is%20carelessness%2C%20carelessness%20is%20selfishness%2C%20and%20selfishness%20is%20sin.%22%20And%20I%20have%20often%20noticed%20among%20college%20girls%20an%20air%20of%20humiliation%20and%20shame%20when%20obliged%20to%20confess%20a%20lack%20of%20physical%20vigor%2C%20as%20if%20they%20were%20convicted%20of%20managing%20life%20with%20bad%20judgment%2C%20or%20of%20some%20moral%20delinquency.%20With%20the%20spreading%20scientific%20conviction%20that%20health%20is%20a%20matter%20largely%20under%20each%20person%26%2339%3Bs%20control%2C%20that%20even%20inherited%20tendencies%20to%20disease%20need%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20run%20their%20riotous%20course%20unchecked%2C%20there%20comes%20an%20earnest%20purpose%20to%20be%20strong%20and%20free.%20Fascinating%20fields%20of%20knowledge%20are%20waiting%20to%20be%20explored%3B%20possibilities%20of%20doing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20knowing%2C%20are%20on%20every%20side%3B%20new%20and%20dear%20friendships%20enlarge%20and%20sweeten%20dreams%20of%20future%20study%20and%20work%2C%20and%20the%20young%20student%20cannot%20afford%20quivering%20nerves%20or%20small%20lungs%20or%20an%20aching%20head%20any%20more%20than%20bad%20taste%2C%20rough%20manners%2C%20or%20a%20weak%20will.%20Handicapped%20by%20inheritance%20or%20bad%20training%2C%20she%20finds%20the%20plan%20of%20college%20life%20itself%20her%20supporter%20and%20friend.%20The%20steady%2C%20long-continued%20routine%20of%20mental%20work%2C%20physical%20exercise%2C%20recreation%2C%20and%20sleep%2C%20the%20simple%20and%20wholesome%20food%2C%20in%20place%20of%20irregular%20and%20unstudied%20diet%2C%20work%20out%20salvation%20for%20her.%20Instead%20of%20being%20left%20to%20go%20out-of-doors%20when%20she%20feels%20like%20it%2C%20the%20regular%20training%20of%20the%20gymnasium%2C%20the%20boats%20on%20lake%20and%20river%2C%20the%20tennis%20court%2C%20the%20golf%20links%2C%20the%20basket%20ball%2C%20the%20bicycle%2C%20the%20long%20walk%20among%20the%20woods%20in%20search%20of%20botanical%20or%20geological%20specimens%2C--all%20these%20and%20many%20more%20call%20to%20the%20busy%20student%2C%20until%20she%20realizes%20that%20they%20have%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20every%20well-ordered%20day%20of%20every%20month.%20So%20she%20learns%2C%20little%20by%20little%2C%20that%20buoyant%20health%20is%20a%20precious%20possession%20to%20be%20won%20and%20kept.%20It%20is%20significant%20that%20already%20statistical%20investigation%20in%20this%20country%20and%20in%20England%20shows%20that%20the%20standard%20of%20health%20is%20higher%20among%20the%20women%20who%20hold%20college%20degrees%20than%20among%20any%20other%20equal%20number%20of%20the%20same%20age%20and%20class.%20And%20it%20is%20interesting%20also%20to%20observe%20to%20what%20sort%20of%20questions%20our%20recent%20girl%20graduates%20have%20been%20inclined%20to%20devote%20attention.%20They%20have%20been%20largely%20the%20neglected%20problems%20of%20little%20children%20and%20their%20health%2C%20of%20home%20sanitation%2C%20of%20food%20and%20its%20choice%20and%20preparation%2C%20of%20domestic%20service%2C%20of%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20schools%20and%20public%20buildings.%20Colleges%20for%20girls%20are%20pledged%20by%20their%20very%20constitution%20to%20make%20persistent%20war%20on%20the%20water%20cure%2C%20the%20nervine%20retreat%2C%20the%20insane%20asylum%2C%20the%20hospital%2C--those%20bitter%20fruits%20of%20the%20emotional%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20women.%20%22I%20can%20never%20afford%20a%20sick%20headache%20again%2C%20life%20is%20so%20interesting%20and%20there%20is%20so%20much%20to%20do%2C%22%20a%20delicate%20girl%20said%20to%20me%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20college%20year.%20And%20while%20her%20mother%20was%20in%20a%20far-off%20invalid%20retreat%2C%20she%20undertook%20the%20battle%20against%20fate%20with%20the%20same%20intelligence%20and%20courage%20which%20she%20put%20into%20her%20calculus%20problems%20and%20her%20translations%20of%20Sophocles.%20Her%20beautiful%20home%20and%20her%20rosy%20and%20happy%20children%20prove%20the%20measure%20of%20her%20hard-won%20success.%20Formerly%20the%20majority%20of%20physicians%20had%20but%20one%20question%20for%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20nervous%20and%20delicate%20girl%2C%20%22Does%20she%20go%20to%20school%3F%22%20And%20only%20one%20prescription%2C%20%22Take%20her%20out%20of%20school.%22%20Never%20a%20suggestion%20as%20to%20suppers%20of%20pickles%20and%20pound-cake%2C%20never%20a%20hint%20about%20midnight%20dancing%20and%20hurried%20day-time%20ways.%20But%20now%20the%20sensible%20doctor%20asks%2C%20%22What%20are%20her%20interests%3F%20What%20are%20her%20tastes%3F%20What%20are%20her%20habits%3F%22%20And%20he%20finds%20new%20interests%20for%20her%2C%20and%20urges%20the%20formation%20of%20out-of-door%20tastes%20and%20steady%20occupation%20for%20the%20mind%2C%20in%20order%20to%20draw%20the%20morbid%20girl%20from%20herself%20into%20the%20invigorating%20world%20outside.%20This%20the%20college%20does%20largely%20through%20its%20third%20gift%20of%20friendship.%20Until%20a%20girl%20goes%20away%20from%20home%20to%20school%20or%20college%2C%20her%20friends%20are%20chiefly%20chosen%20for%20her%20by%20circumstances.%20Her%20young%20relatives%2C%20her%20neighbors%20in%20the%20same%20street%2C%20those%20who%20happen%20to%20go%20to%20the%20same%20school%20or%20church%2C--these%20she%20makes%20her%20girlish%20intimates.%20She%20goes%20to%20college%20with%20the%20entire%20conviction%2C%20half%20unknown%20to%20herself%2C%20that%20her%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20political%20party%20contains%20all%20the%20honest%20men%2C%20her%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20circle%20all%20the%20true%20ladies%2C%20her%20church%20all%20the%20real%20saints%20of%20the%20community.%20And%20the%20smaller%20the%20town%2C%20the%20more%20absolute%20is%20her%20belief.%20But%20in%20college%20she%20finds%20that%20the%20girl%20who%20earned%20her%20scholarship%20in%20the%20village%20school%20sits%20beside%20the%20banker%26%2339%3Bs%20daughter%3B%20the%20New%20England%20farmer%26%2339%3Bs%20child%20rooms%20next%20the%20heiress%20of%20a%20Hawaiian%20sugar%20plantation%3B%20the%20daughters%20of%20the%20opposing%20candidates%20in%20a%20sharply%20fought%20election%20have%20grown%20great%20friends%20in%20college%20boats%20and%20laboratories%3B%20and%20before%20her%20diploma%20is%20won%20she%20realizes%20how%20much%20richer%20a%20world%20she%20lives%20in%20than%20she%20ever%20dreamed%20of%20at%20home.%20The%20wealth%20that%20lies%20in%20differences%20has%20dawned%20upon%20her%20vision.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%20sit%20down%20together%20that%20either%20can%20understand%20how%20the%20Lord%20is%20the%20Maker%20of%20them%20all.%20To-day%20above%20all%20things%20we%20need%20the%20influence%20of%20men%20and%20women%20of%20friendliness%2C%20of%20generous%20nature%2C%20of%20hospitality%20to%20new%20ideas%2C%20in%20short%2C%20of%20social%20imagination.%20But%20instead%2C%20we%20find%20each%20political%20party%20bitterly%20calling%20the%20other%20dishonest%2C%20each%20class%20suspicious%20of%20the%20intentions%20of%20the%20other%2C%20and%20in%20social%20life%20the%20pettiest%20standards%20of%20conduct.%20Is%20it%20not%20well%20for%20us%20that%20the%20colleges%20all%20over%20the%20country%20still%20offer%20to%20their%20fortunate%20students%20a%20society%20of%20the%20most%20democratic%20sort%2C--one%20in%20which%20a%20father%26%2339%3Bs%20money%2C%20a%20mother%26%2339%3Bs%20social%20position%2C%20can%20assure%20no%20distinction%20and%20make%20no%20close%20friends%3F%20Here%20capacity%20of%20every%20kind%20counts%20for%20its%20full%20value.%20Here%20enthusiasm%20waits%20to%20make%20heroes%20of%20those%20who%20can%20lead.%20Here%20charming%20manners%2C%20noble%20character%2C%20amiable%20temper%2C%20scholarly%20power%2C%20find%20their%20full%20opportunity%20and%20inspire%20such%20friendships%20as%20are%20seldom%20made%20afterward.%20I%20have%20forgotten%20my%20chemistry%2C%20and%20my%20classical%20philology%20cannot%20bear%20examination%3B%20but%20all%20round%20the%20world%20there%20are%20men%20and%20women%20at%20work%2C%20my%20intimates%20of%20college%20days%2C%20who%20have%20made%20the%20wide%20earth%20a%20friendly%20place%20to%20me.%20Of%20every%20creed%2C%20of%20every%20party%2C%20in%20far-away%20places%20and%20in%20near%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20them%20makes%20me%20more%20courageous%20in%20duty%20and%20more%20faithful%20to%20opportunity%2C%20though%20for%20many%20years%20we%20may%20not%20have%20had%20time%20to%20write%20each%20other%20a%20letter.%20The%20basis%20of%20all%20valuable%20and%20enduring%20friendships%20is%20not%20accident%20or%20juxtaposition%2C%20but%20tastes%2C%20interests%2C%20habits%2C%20work%2C%20ambitions.%20It%20is%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20to%20college%20friendship%20clings%20a%20romance%20entirely%20its%20own.%20One%20of%20the%20friends%20may%20spend%20her%20days%20in%20the%20laboratory%2C%20eagerly%20chasing%20the%20shy%20facts%20that%20hide%20beyond%20the%20microscope%26%2339%3Bs%20fine%20vision%2C%20and%20the%20other%20may%20fill%20her%20hours%20and%20her%20heart%20with%20the%20poets%20and%20the%20philosophers%3B%20one%20may%20steadfastly%20pursue%20her%20way%20toward%20the%20command%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20other%20towards%20the%20world%20of%20letters%20and%20of%20art%3B%20these%20divergences%20constitute%20no%20barrier%2C%20but%20rather%20an%20aid%20to%20the%20fulness%20of%20friendship.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20goes%20in%20a%20simple%20gown%20which%20she%20has%20earned%20and%20made%20herself%2C%20and%20the%20other%20lives%20when%20at%20home%20in%20a%20merchant%26%2339%3Bs%20modern%20palace--what%20has%20that%20to%20do%20with%20the%20things%20the%20girls%20care%20about%20and%20the%20dreams%20they%20talk%20over%20in%20the%20walk%20by%20the%20river%20or%20the%20bicycle%20ride%20through%20country%20roads%3F%20If%20any%20young%20man%20to-day%20goes%20through%20Harvard%20lonely%2C%20neglected%2C%20unfriended%2C%20if%20any%20girl%20lives%20solitary%20and%20wretched%20in%20her%20life%20at%20Wellesley%2C%20it%20is%20their%20own%20fault.%20It%20must%20be%20because%20they%20are%20suspicious%2C%20unfriendly%20or%20disagreeable%20themselves.%20Certainly%20it%20is%20true%20that%20in%20the%20associations%20of%20college%20life%2C%20more%20than